var book = {
	"name": "Job",
	"numChapters": 42,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>There was a man in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12871A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12871A\"></sup>land of Uz whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12871B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12871B\"></sup>Job; and that man was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12871C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12871C\"></sup>blameless, upright, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12871D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12871D\"></sup>fearing God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12871E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12871E\"></sup>turning away from evil.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12872F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12872F\"></sup>Seven sons and three daughters were born to him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12873G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12873G\"></sup>His possessions also were 7,000 sheep, 3,000 camels, 500 yoke of oxen, 500 female donkeys, and very many servants; and that man was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12873H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12873H\"></sup>the greatest of all the men of the east.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His sons used to go and hold a feast in the house of each one on his day, and they would send and invite their three sisters to eat and drink with them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the days of feasting had completed their cycle, Job would send and consecrate them, rising up early in the morning and offering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12875I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12875I\"></sup>burnt offerings <i>according to</i> the number of them all; for Job said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12875J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12875J\"></sup>Perhaps my sons have sinned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12875K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12875K\"></sup>cursed God in their hearts.” Thus Job did continually.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12876L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12876L\"></sup>Now there was a day when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12876M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12876M\"></sup>sons of God came to present themselves before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and Satan also came among them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “From where do you come?” Then Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12877N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12877N\"></sup>From roaming about on the earth and walking around on it.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Have you considered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12878O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12878O\"></sup>My servant Job? For there is no one like him on the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12878P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12878P\"></sup>a blameless and upright man, fearing God and turning away from evil.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12879Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12879Q\"></sup>Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Does Job fear God for nothing?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12880R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12880R\"></sup>Have You not made a hedge about him and his house and all that he has, on every side? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12880S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12880S\"></sup>You have blessed the work of his hands, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12880T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12880T\"></sup>possessions have increased in the land.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12881U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12881U\"></sup>But put forth Your hand now and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12881V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12881V\"></sup>touch all that he has; he will surely curse You to Your face.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Behold, all that he has is in your power, only do not put forth your hand on him.” So Satan departed from the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now on the day when his sons and his daughters were eating and drinking wine in their oldest brother’s house,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>a messenger came to Job and said, “The oxen were plowing and the donkeys feeding beside them,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12885W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12885W\"></sup>Sabeans attacked and took them. They also slew the servants with the edge of the sword, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>While he was still speaking, another also came and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12886X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12886X\"></sup>The fire of God fell from heaven and burned up the sheep and the servants and consumed them, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>While he was still speaking, another also came and said, “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12887Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12887Y\"></sup>Chaldeans formed three bands and made a raid on the camels and took them and slew the servants with the edge of the sword, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>While he was still speaking, another also came and said, “Your sons and your daughters were eating and drinking wine in their oldest brother’s house,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and behold, a great wind came from across the wilderness and struck the four corners of the house, and it fell on the young people and they died, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then Job arose and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12890Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12890Z\"></sup>tore his robe and shaved his head, and he fell to the ground and worshiped.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12891AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12891AA\"></sup>Naked I came from my mother’s womb,And naked I shall return there.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12891AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12891AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has taken away.Blessed be the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12892AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12892AC\"></sup>Through all this Job did not sin nor did he blame God."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12893A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12893A\"></sup>Again there was a day when the sons of God came to present themselves before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and Satan also came among them to present himself before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Where have you come from?” Then Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “From roaming about on the earth and walking around on it.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Have you considered My servant Job? For there is no one like him on the earth, a blameless and upright man fearing God and turning away from evil. And he still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12895B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12895B\"></sup>holds fast his integrity, although you incited Me against him to ruin him without cause.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “Skin for skin! Yes, all that a man has he will give for his life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12897C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12897C\"></sup>However, put forth Your hand now, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12897D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12897D\"></sup>touch his bone and his flesh; he will curse You to Your face.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Behold, he is in your power, only spare his life.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then Satan went out from the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and smote Job with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12899E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12899E\"></sup>sore boils from the sole of his foot to the crown of his head.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he took a potsherd to scrape himself while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12900F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12900F\"></sup>he was sitting among the ashes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then his wife said to him, “Do you still hold fast your integrity? Curse God and die!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But he said to her, “You speak as one of the foolish women speaks. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12902G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12902G\"></sup>Shall we indeed accept good from God and not accept adversity?” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12902H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12902H\"></sup>In all this Job did not sin with his lips.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now when Job’s three friends heard of all this adversity that had come upon him, they came each one from his own place, Eliphaz the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12903I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12903I\"></sup>Temanite, Bildad the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12903J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12903J\"></sup>Shuhite and Zophar the Naamathite; and they made an appointment together to come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12903K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12903K\"></sup>sympathize with him and comfort him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When they lifted up their eyes at a distance and did not recognize him, they raised their voices and wept. And each of them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12904L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12904L\"></sup>tore his robe and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12904M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12904M\"></sup>threw dust over their heads toward the sky.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12905N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12905N\"></sup>Then they sat down on the ground with him for seven days and seven nights with no one speaking a word to him, for they saw that <i>his</i> pain was very great."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Afterward Job opened his mouth and cursed the day of his <i>birth</i>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Job said,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12908A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12908A\"></sup>Let the day perish on which I was to be born,And the night <i>which</i> said, ‘A boy is conceived.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“May that day be darkness;Let not God above care for it,Nor light shine on it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12910B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12910B\"></sup>darkness and black gloom claim it;Let a cloud settle on it;Let the blackness of the day terrify it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<i>As for</i> that night, let darkness seize it;Let it not rejoice among the days of the year;Let it not come into the number of the months.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Behold, let that night be barren;Let no joyful shout enter it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Let those curse it who curse the day,Who are prepared to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12913C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12913C\"></sup>rouse Leviathan.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Let the stars of its twilight be darkened;Let it wait for light but have none,And let it not see the breaking dawn;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Because it did not shut the opening of my <i>mother’s</i> womb,Or hide trouble from my eyes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12916D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12916D\"></sup>Why did I not die at birth,Come forth from the womb and expire?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Why did the knees receive me,And why the breasts, that I should suck?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“For now I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12918E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12918E\"></sup>would have lain down and been quiet;I would have slept then, I would have been at rest,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12919F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12919F\"></sup>kings and <i>with</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12919G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12919G\"></sup>counselors of the earth,Who rebuilt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12919H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12919H\"></sup>ruins for themselves;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Or with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12920I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12920I\"></sup>princes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12920J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12920J\"></sup>who had gold,Who were filling their houses <i>with</i> silver.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Or like a miscarriage which is discarded, I would not be,As infants that never saw light.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“There the wicked cease from raging,And there the weary are at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12922K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12922K\"></sup>rest.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“The prisoners are at ease together;They do not hear the voice of the taskmaster.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“The small and the great are there,And the slave is free from his master.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Why is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12925L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12925L\"></sup>light given to him who suffers,And life to the bitter of soul,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12926M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12926M\"></sup>long for death, but there is none,And dig for it more than for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12926N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12926N\"></sup>hidden treasures,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Who rejoice greatly,<i>And</i> exult when they find the grave?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<i>Why is light given</i> to a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12928O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12928O\"></sup>whose way is hidden,And whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12928P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12928P\"></sup>God has hedged in?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12929Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12929Q\"></sup>my groaning comes at the sight of my food,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12929R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12929R\"></sup>my cries pour out like water.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12930S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12930S\"></sup>what I fear comes upon me,And what I dread befalls me.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12931T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12931T\"></sup>am not at ease, nor am I quiet,And I am not at rest, but turmoil comes.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“If one ventures a word with you, will you become impatient?But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12933A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12933A\"></sup>who can refrain from speaking?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Behold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12934B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12934B\"></sup>you have admonished many,And you have strengthened weak hands.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Your words have helped the tottering to stand,And you have strengthened feeble knees.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“But now it has come to you, and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12936C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12936C\"></sup>are impatient;It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12936D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12936D\"></sup>touches you, and you are dismayed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Is not your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12937E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12937E\"></sup>fear <i>of God</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12937F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12937F\"></sup>your confidence,And the integrity of your ways your hope?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Remember now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12938G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12938G\"></sup>who <i>ever</i> perished being innocent?Or where were the upright destroyed?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“According to what I have seen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12939H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12939H\"></sup>those who plow iniquityAnd those who sow trouble harvest it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12940I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12940I\"></sup>the breath of God they perish,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12940J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12940J\"></sup>by the blast of His anger they come to an end.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12941K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12941K\"></sup>roaring of the lion and the voice of the <i>fierce</i> lion,And the teeth of the young lions are broken.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12942L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12942L\"></sup>lion perishes for lack of prey,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12942M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12942M\"></sup>whelps of the lioness are scattered.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Now a word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12943N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12943N\"></sup>was brought to me stealthily,And my ear received a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12943O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12943O\"></sup>whisper of it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Amid disquieting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12944P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12944P\"></sup>thoughts from the visions of the night,When deep sleep falls on men,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Dread came upon me, and trembling,And made all my bones shake.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Then a spirit passed by my face;The hair of my flesh bristled up.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“It stood still, but I could not discern its appearance;A form <i>was</i> before my eyes;<i>There was</i> silence, then I heard a voice:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12948Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12948Q\"></sup>mankind be just before God?Can a man be pure before his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12948R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12948R\"></sup>Maker?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12949S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12949S\"></sup>He puts no trust even in His servants;And against His angels He charges error.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘How much more those who dwell in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12950T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12950T\"></sup>houses of clay,Whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12950U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12950U\"></sup>foundation is in the dust,Who are crushed before the moth!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12951V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12951V\"></sup>Between morning and evening they are broken in pieces;Unobserved, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12951W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12951W\"></sup>perish forever.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>‘Is not their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12952X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12952X\"></sup>tent-cord plucked up within them?They die, yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12952Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12952Y\"></sup>without wisdom.’"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Call now, is there anyone who will answer you?And to which of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12953A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12953A\"></sup>holy ones will you turn?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12954B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12954B\"></sup>anger slays the foolish man,And jealousy kills the simple.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I have seen the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12955C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12955C\"></sup>foolish taking root,And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12955D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12955D\"></sup>cursed his abode immediately.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12956E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12956E\"></sup>sons are far from safety,They are even oppressed in the gate,And there is no deliverer.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“His harvest the hungry devourAnd take it to a <i>place of</i> thorns,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12957F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12957F\"></sup>schemer is eager for their wealth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12958G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12958G\"></sup>affliction does not come from the dust,Nor does trouble sprout from the ground,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12959H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12959H\"></sup>man is born for trouble,As sparks fly upward.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But as for me, I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12960I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12960I\"></sup>seek God,And I would place my cause before God;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12961J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12961J\"></sup>does great and unsearchable things,Wonders without number.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12962K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12962K\"></sup>gives rain on the earthAnd sends water on the fields,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12963L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12963L\"></sup>He sets on high those who are lowly,And those who mourn are lifted to safety.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12964M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12964M\"></sup>frustrates the plotting of the shrewd,So that their hands cannot attain success.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12965N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12965N\"></sup>captures the wise by their own shrewdness,And the advice of the cunning is quickly thwarted.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“By day they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12966O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12966O\"></sup>meet with darkness,And grope at noon as in the night.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“But He saves from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12967P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12967P\"></sup>the sword of their mouth,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12967Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12967Q\"></sup>the poor from the hand of the mighty.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“So the helpless has hope,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12968R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12968R\"></sup>unrighteousness must shut its mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Behold, how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12969S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12969S\"></sup>happy is the man whom God reproves,So do not despise the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12969T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12969T\"></sup>discipline of the Almighty.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12970U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12970U\"></sup>He inflicts pain, and gives relief;He wounds, and His hands <i>also</i> heal.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“From six troubles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12971V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12971V\"></sup>He will deliver you,Even in seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12971W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12971W\"></sup>evil will not touch you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12972X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12972X\"></sup>famine He will redeem you from death,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12972Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12972Y\"></sup>in war from the power of the sword.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“You will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12973Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12973Z\"></sup>hidden from the scourge of the tongue,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12973AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12973AA\"></sup>And you will not be afraid of violence when it comes.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12974AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12974AB\"></sup>laugh at violence and famine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12974AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12974AC\"></sup>And you will not be afraid of wild beasts.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“For you will be in league with the stones of the field,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12975AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12975AD\"></sup>the beasts of the field will be at peace with you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“You will know that your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12976AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12976AE\"></sup>tent is secure,For you will visit your abode and fear no loss.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“You will know also that your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12977AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12977AF\"></sup>descendants will be many,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12977AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12977AG\"></sup>your offspring as the grass of the earth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12978AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12978AH\"></sup>come to the grave in full vigor,Like the stacking of grain in its season.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Behold this; we have investigated it, <i>and</i> so it is.Hear it, and know for yourself.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Then Job answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12981A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12981A\"></sup>Oh that my grief were actually weighedAnd laid in the balances together with my calamity!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For then it would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12982B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12982B\"></sup>heavier than the sand of the seas;Therefore my words have been rash.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12983C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12983C\"></sup>arrows of the Almighty are within me,Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12983D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12983D\"></sup>poison my spirit drinks;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12983E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12983E\"></sup>terrors of God are arrayed against me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Does the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12984F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12984F\"></sup>wild donkey bray over <i>his</i> grass,Or does the ox low over his fodder?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Can something tasteless be eaten without salt,Or is there any taste in the white of an egg?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“My soul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12986G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12986G\"></sup>refuses to touch <i>them</i>;They are like loathsome food to me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Oh that my request might come to pass,And that God would grant my longing!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Would that God were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12988H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12988H\"></sup>willing to crush me,That He would loose His hand and cut me off!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But it is still my consolation,And I rejoice in unsparing pain,That I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12989I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12989I\"></sup>have not denied the words of the Holy One.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“What is my strength, that I should wait?And what is my end, that I should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12990J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12990J\"></sup>endure?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Is my strength the strength of stones,Or is my flesh bronze?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Is it that my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12992K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12992K\"></sup>help is not within me,And that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12992L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12992L\"></sup>deliverance is driven from me?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12993M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12993M\"></sup>despairing man <i>there should be</i> kindness from his friend;So that he does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12993N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12993N\"></sup>forsake the fear of the Almighty.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“My brothers have acted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12994O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12994O\"></sup>deceitfully like a wadi,Like the torrents of wadis which vanish,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Which are turbid because of ice<i>And</i> into which the snow melts.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12996P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12996P\"></sup>they become waterless, they are silent,When it is hot, they vanish from their place.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“The paths of their course wind along,They go up into nothing and perish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“The caravans of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12998Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12998Q\"></sup>Tema looked,The travelers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12998R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12998R\"></sup>Sheba hoped for them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-12999S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-12999S\"></sup>were disappointed for they had trusted,They came there and were confounded.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Indeed, you have now become such,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13000T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13000T\"></sup>You see a terror and are afraid.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Have I said, ‘Give me <i>something</i>,’Or, ‘Offer a bribe for me from your wealth,’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Or, ‘Deliver me from the hand of the adversary,’Or, ‘Redeem me from the hand of the tyrants’?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Teach me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13003U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13003U\"></sup>I will be silent;And show me how I have erred.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“How painful are honest words!But what does your argument prove?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Do you intend to reprove <i>my</i> words,When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13005V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13005V\"></sup>words of one in despair belong to the wind?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“You would even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13006W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13006W\"></sup>cast <i>lots</i> for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13006X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13006X\"></sup>the orphansAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13006Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13006Y\"></sup>barter over your friend.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Now please look at me,And <i>see</i> if I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13007Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13007Z\"></sup>lie to your face.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Desist now, let there be no injustice;Even desist, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13008AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13008AA\"></sup>my righteousness is yet in it.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Is there injustice on my tongue?Cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13009AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13009AB\"></sup>my palate discern calamities?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>“Is not man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13010A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13010A\"></sup>forced to labor on earth,And <i>are not</i> his days like the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13010B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13010B\"></sup>a hired man?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“As a slave who pants for the shade,And as a hired man who eagerly waits for his wages,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So am I allotted months of vanity,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13012C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13012C\"></sup>nights of trouble are appointed me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13013D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13013D\"></sup>lie down I say,‘When shall I arise?’But the night continues,And I am continually tossing until dawn.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13014E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13014E\"></sup>flesh is clothed with worms and a crust of dirt,My skin hardens and runs.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“My days are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13015F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13015F\"></sup>swifter than a weaver’s shuttle,And come to an end <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13015G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13015G\"></sup>without hope.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Remember that my life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13016H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13016H\"></sup>is <i>but</i> breath;My eye will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13016I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13016I\"></sup>not again see good.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13017J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13017J\"></sup>eye of him who sees me will behold me no longer;Your eyes <i>will be</i> on me, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13017K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13017K\"></sup>I will not be.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“When a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13018L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13018L\"></sup>cloud vanishes, it is gone,So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13018M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13018M\"></sup>he who goes down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13018N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13018N\"></sup>Sheol does not come up.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He will not return again to his house,Nor will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13019O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13019O\"></sup>his place know him anymore.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13020P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13020P\"></sup>I will not restrain my mouth;I will speak in the anguish of my spirit,I will complain in the bitterness of my soul.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Am I the sea, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13021Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13021Q\"></sup>the sea monster,That You set a guard over me?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If I say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13022R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13022R\"></sup>My bed will comfort me,My couch will ease my complaint,’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then You frighten me with dreamsAnd terrify me by visions;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So that my soul would choose suffocation,Death rather than my pains.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13025S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13025S\"></sup>waste away; I will not live forever.Leave me alone, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13025T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13025T\"></sup>for my days are <i>but</i> a breath.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13026U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13026U\"></sup>What is man that You magnify him,And that You are concerned about him,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13027V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13027V\"></sup>You examine him every morningAnd try him every moment?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13028W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13028W\"></sup>Will You never turn Your gaze away from me,Nor let me alone until I swallow my spittle?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13029X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13029X\"></sup>Have I sinned? What have I done to You,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13029Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13029Y\"></sup>watcher of men?Why have You set me as Your target,So that I am a burden to myself?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Why then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13030Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13030Z\"></sup>do You not pardon my transgressionAnd take away my iniquity?For now I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13030AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13030AA\"></sup>lie down in the dust;And You will seek me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13030AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13030AB\"></sup>but I will not be.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Then Bildad the Shuhite answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you say these things,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13032A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13032A\"></sup>words of your mouth be a mighty wind?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13033B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13033B\"></sup>God pervert justice?Or does the Almighty pervert what is right?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13034C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13034C\"></sup>If your sons sinned against Him,Then He delivered them into the power of their transgression.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13035D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13035D\"></sup>seek GodAnd implore the compassion of the Almighty,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If you are pure and upright,Surely now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13036E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13036E\"></sup>He would rouse Himself for youAnd restore your righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13036F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13036F\"></sup>estate.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Though your beginning was insignificant,Yet your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13037G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13037G\"></sup>end will increase greatly.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Please <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13038H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13038H\"></sup>inquire of past generations,And consider the things searched out by their fathers.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For we are <i>only</i> of yesterday and know nothing,Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13039I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13039I\"></sup>our days on earth are as a shadow.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Will they not teach you <i>and</i> tell you,And bring forth words from their minds?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Can the papyrus grow up without a marsh?Can the rushes grow without water?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“While it is still green <i>and</i> not cut down,Yet it withers before any <i>other</i> plant.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“So are the paths of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13043J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13043J\"></sup>all who forget God;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13043K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13043K\"></sup>hope of the godless will perish,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Whose confidence is fragile,And whose trust a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13044L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13044L\"></sup>spider’s web.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“He trusts in his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13045M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13045M\"></sup>house, but it does not stand;He holds fast to it, but it does not endure.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13046N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13046N\"></sup>thrives before the sun,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13046O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13046O\"></sup>shoots spread out over his garden.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“His roots wrap around a rock pile,He grasps a house of stones.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“If he is removed from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13048P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13048P\"></sup>his place,Then it will deny him, <i>saying</i>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13048Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13048Q\"></sup>I never saw you.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13049R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13049R\"></sup>this is the joy of His way;And out of the dust others will spring.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Lo, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13050S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13050S\"></sup>God will not reject <i>a man of</i> integrity,Nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13050T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13050T\"></sup>will He support the evildoers.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“He will yet fill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13051U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13051U\"></sup>your mouth with laughterAnd your lips with shouting.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Those who hate you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13052V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13052V\"></sup>clothed with shame,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13052W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13052W\"></sup>tent of the wicked will be no longer.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Then Job answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“In truth I know that this is so;But how can a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13054A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13054A\"></sup>man be in the right before God?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“If one wished to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13055B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13055B\"></sup>dispute with Him,He could not answer Him once in a thousand <i>times</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13056C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13056C\"></sup>Wise in heart and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13056D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13056D\"></sup>mighty in strength,Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13056E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13056E\"></sup>defied Him without harm?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13057F\"></sup><i>It is God</i> who removes the mountains, they know not <i>how</i>,When He overturns them in His anger;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13058G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13058G\"></sup>shakes the earth out of its place,And its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13058H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13058H\"></sup>pillars tremble;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Who commands the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13059I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13059I\"></sup>sun not to shine,And sets a seal upon the stars;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who alone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13060J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13060J\"></sup>stretches out the heavensAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13060K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13060K\"></sup>tramples down the waves of the sea;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Who makes the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13061L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13061L\"></sup>Bear, Orion and the Pleiades,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13061M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13061M\"></sup>chambers of the south;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13062N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13062N\"></sup>does great things, unfathomable,And wondrous works without number.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Were He to pass by me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13063O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13063O\"></sup>I would not see Him;Were He to move past <i>me</i>, I would not perceive Him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Were He to snatch away, who could <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13064P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13064P\"></sup>restrain Him?Who could say to Him, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13064Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13064Q\"></sup>What are You doing?’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“God will not turn back His anger;Beneath Him crouch the helpers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13065R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13065R\"></sup>Rahab.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“How then can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13066S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13066S\"></sup>I answer Him,<i>And</i> choose my words before Him?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13067T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13067T\"></sup>though I were right, I could not answer;I would have to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13067U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13067U\"></sup>implore the mercy of my judge.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“If I called and He answered me,I could not believe that He was listening to my voice.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13069V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13069V\"></sup>bruises me with a tempestAnd multiplies my wounds without cause.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13070W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13070W\"></sup>not allow me to get my breath,But saturates me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13070X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13070X\"></sup>bitterness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“If <i>it is a matter</i> of power, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13071Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13071Y\"></sup>behold, <i>He is</i> the strong one!And if <i>it is a matter</i> of justice, who can summon Him?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13072Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13072Z\"></sup>Though I am righteous, my mouth will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13072AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13072AA\"></sup>condemn me;Though I am guiltless, He will declare me guilty.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13073AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13073AB\"></sup>guiltless;I do not take notice of myself;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13073AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13073AC\"></sup>despise my life.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“It is <i>all</i> one; therefore I say,‘He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13074AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13074AD\"></sup>destroys the guiltless and the wicked.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“If the scourge kills suddenly,He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13075AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13075AE\"></sup>mocks the despair of the innocent.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“The earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13076AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13076AF\"></sup>is given into the hand of the wicked;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13076AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13076AG\"></sup>covers the faces of its judges.If <i>it is</i> not <i>He</i>, then who is it?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13077AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13077AH\"></sup>my days are swifter than a runner;They flee away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13077AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13077AI\"></sup>they see no good.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“They slip by like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13078AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13078AJ\"></sup>reed boats,Like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13078AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13078AK\"></sup>eagle that swoops on its prey.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Though I say, ‘I will forget <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13079AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13079AL\"></sup>my complaint,I will leave off my <i>sad</i> countenance and be cheerful,’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13080AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13080AM\"></sup>afraid of all my pains,I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13080AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13080AN\"></sup>You will not acquit me.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“I am accounted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13081AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13081AO\"></sup>wicked,Why then should I toil in vain?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“If I should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13082AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13082AP\"></sup>wash myself with snowAnd cleanse <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13082AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13082AQ\"></sup>my hands with lye,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Yet You would plunge me into the pit,And my own clothes would abhor me.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13084AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13084AR\"></sup><i>He is</i> not a man as I am that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13084AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13084AS\"></sup>I may answer Him,That we may go to court together.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“There is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13085AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13085AT\"></sup>umpire between us,Who may lay his hand upon us both.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Let Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13086AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13086AU\"></sup>remove His rod from me,And let not dread of Him terrify me.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“<i>Then</i> I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13087AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13087AV\"></sup>would speak and not fear Him;But I am not like that in myself."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13088A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13088A\"></sup>I loathe my own life;I will give full vent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13088B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13088B\"></sup>my complaint;I will speak in the bitterness of my soul.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I will say to God, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13089C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13089C\"></sup>Do not condemn me;Let me know why You contend with me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘Is it right for You indeed to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13090D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13090D\"></sup>oppress,To reject <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13090E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13090E\"></sup>the labor of Your hands,And to look favorably on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13090F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13090F\"></sup>the schemes of the wicked?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘Have You eyes of flesh?Or do You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13091G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13091G\"></sup>see as a man sees?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>‘Are Your days as the days of a mortal,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13092H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13092H\"></sup>Your years as man’s years,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13093I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13093I\"></sup>You should seek for my guiltAnd search after my sin?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘According to Your knowledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13094J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13094J\"></sup>I am indeed not guilty,Yet there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13094K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13094K\"></sup>no deliverance from Your hand.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13095L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13095L\"></sup>Your hands fashioned and made me altogether,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13095M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13095M\"></sup>And would You destroy me?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘Remember now, that You have made me as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13096N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13096N\"></sup>clay;And would You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13096O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13096O\"></sup>turn me into dust again?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Did You not pour me out like milkAnd curdle me like cheese;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Clothe me with skin and flesh,And knit me together with bones and sinews?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13099P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13099P\"></sup>granted me life and lovingkindness;And Your care has preserved my spirit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13100Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13100Q\"></sup>these things You have concealed in Your heart;I know that this is within You:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If I sin, then You would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13101R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13101R\"></sup>take note of me,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13101S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13101S\"></sup>would not acquit me of my guilt.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13102T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13102T\"></sup>I am wicked, woe to me!And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13102U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13102U\"></sup>if I am righteous, I dare not lift up my head.<i>I am</i> sated with disgrace and conscious of my misery.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>‘Should <i>my head</i> be lifted up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13103V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13103V\"></sup>You would hunt me like a lion;And again You would show Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13103W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13103W\"></sup>power against me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘You renew <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13104X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13104X\"></sup>Your witnesses against meAnd increase Your anger toward me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13104Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13104Y\"></sup>Hardship after hardship is with me.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13105Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13105Z\"></sup>Why then have You brought me out of the womb?Would that I had died and no eye had seen me!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘I should have been as though I had not been,Carried from womb to tomb.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Would He not let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13107AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13107AA\"></sup>my few days alone?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13107AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13107AB\"></sup>Withdraw from me that I may have a little cheer",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Before I go—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13108AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13108AC\"></sup>and I shall not return—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13108AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13108AD\"></sup>To the land of darkness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13108AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13108AE\"></sup>deep shadow,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The land of utter gloom as darkness <i>itself</i>,Of deep shadow without order,And which shines as the darkness.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then Zophar the Naamathite answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Shall a multitude of words go unanswered,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13111A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13111A\"></sup>talkative man be acquitted?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Shall your boasts silence men?And shall you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13112B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13112B\"></sup>scoff and none rebuke?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13113C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13113C\"></sup>you have said, ‘My teaching is pure,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13113D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13113D\"></sup>I am innocent in your eyes.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“But would that God might speak,And open His lips against you,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And show you the secrets of wisdom!For sound wisdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13115E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13115E\"></sup>has two sides.Know then that God forgets a part of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13115F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13115F\"></sup>your iniquity.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13116G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13116G\"></sup>Can you discover the depths of God?Can you discover the limits of the Almighty?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<i>They are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13117H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13117H\"></sup>high as the heavens, what can you do?Deeper than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13117I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13117I\"></sup>Sheol, what can you know?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Its measure is longer than the earthAnd broader than the sea.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“If He passes by or shuts up,Or calls an assembly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13119J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13119J\"></sup>who can restrain Him?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13120K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13120K\"></sup>He knows false men,And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13120L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13120L\"></sup>sees iniquity without investigating.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13121M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13121M\"></sup>An idiot will become intelligentWhen the foal of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13121N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13121N\"></sup>wild donkey is born a man.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13122O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13122O\"></sup>If you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13122P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13122P\"></sup>direct your heart rightAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13122Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13122Q\"></sup>spread out your hand to Him,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If iniquity is in your hand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13123R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13123R\"></sup>put it far away,And do not let wickedness dwell in your tents;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Then, indeed, you could <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13124S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13124S\"></sup>lift up your face without <i>moral</i> defect,And you would be steadfast and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13124T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13124T\"></sup>not fear.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13125U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13125U\"></sup>forget <i>your</i> trouble,As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13125V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13125V\"></sup>waters that have passed by, you would remember <i>it</i>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Your life would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13126W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13126W\"></sup>brighter than noonday;Darkness would be like the morning.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Then you would trust, because there is hope;And you would look around and rest securely.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“You would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13128X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13128X\"></sup>lie down and none would disturb <i>you</i>,And many would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13128Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13128Y\"></sup>entreat your favor.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13129Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13129Z\"></sup>eyes of the wicked will fail,And there will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13129AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13129AA\"></sup>be no escape for them;And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13129AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13129AB\"></sup>hope is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13129AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13129AC\"></sup>to breathe their last.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Then Job responded,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Truly then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13131A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13131A\"></sup>you are the people,And with you wisdom will die!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13132B\"></sup>I have intelligence as well as you;I am not inferior to you.And who does not know such things as these?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I am a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13133C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13133C\"></sup>joke to my friends,The one who called on God and He answered him;The just <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13133D\"></sup>blameless <i>man</i> is a joke.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“He who is at ease holds calamity in contempt,As prepared for those whose feet slip.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13135E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13135E\"></sup>tents of the destroyers prosper,And those who provoke God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13135F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13135F\"></sup>are secure,Whom God brings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13135G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13135G\"></sup>into their power.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But now ask the beasts, and let them teach you;And the birds of the heavens, and let them tell you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Or speak to the earth, and let it teach you;And let the fish of the sea declare to you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Who among all these does not knowThat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13138H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13138H\"></sup>the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13139I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13139I\"></sup>In whose hand is the life of every living thing,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13139J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13139J\"></sup>the breath of all mankind?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13140K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13140K\"></sup>the ear test words,As the palate tastes its food?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Wisdom is with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13141L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13141L\"></sup>aged men,<i>With</i> long life is understanding.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“With Him are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13142M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13142M\"></sup>wisdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13142N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13142N\"></sup>might;To Him belong counsel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13142O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13142O\"></sup>understanding.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Behold, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13143P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13143P\"></sup>tears down, and it cannot be rebuilt;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13143Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13143Q\"></sup>imprisons a man, and there can be no release.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Behold, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13144R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13144R\"></sup>restrains the waters, and they dry up;And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13144S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13144S\"></sup>sends them out, and they inundate the earth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“With Him are strength and sound wisdom,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13145T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13145T\"></sup>misled and the misleader belong to Him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“He makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13146U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13146U\"></sup>counselors walk barefootAnd makes fools of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13146V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13146V\"></sup>judges.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13147W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13147W\"></sup>loosens the bond of kingsAnd binds their loins with a girdle.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He makes priests walk barefootAnd overthrows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13148X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13148X\"></sup>the secure ones.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“He deprives the trusted ones of speechAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13149Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13149Y\"></sup>takes away the discernment of the elders.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13150Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13150Z\"></sup>pours contempt on noblesAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13150AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13150AA\"></sup>loosens the belt of the strong.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13151AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13151AB\"></sup>reveals mysteries from the darknessAnd brings the deep darkness into light.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13152AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13152AC\"></sup>makes the nations great, then destroys them;He enlarges the nations, then leads them away.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13153AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13153AD\"></sup>deprives of intelligence the chiefs of the earth’s peopleAnd makes them wander in a pathless waste.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13154AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13154AE\"></sup>grope in darkness with no light,And He makes them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13154AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13154AF\"></sup>stagger like a drunken man."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13155A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13155A\"></sup>Behold, my eye has seen all <i>this</i>,My ear has heard and understood it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13156B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13156B\"></sup>What you know I also know;I am not inferior to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13157C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13157C\"></sup>I would speak to the Almighty,And I desire to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13157D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13157D\"></sup>argue with God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“But you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13158E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13158E\"></sup>smear with lies;You are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13158F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13158F\"></sup>worthless physicians.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“O that you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13159G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13159G\"></sup>be completely silent,And that it would become your wisdom!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Please hear my argumentAnd listen to the contentions of my lips.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13161H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13161H\"></sup>speak what is unjust for God,And speak what is deceitful for Him?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13162I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13162I\"></sup>show partiality for Him?Will you contend for God?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Will it be well when He examines you?Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13163J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13163J\"></sup>will you deceive Him as one deceives a man?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He will surely reprove youIf you secretly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13164K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13164K\"></sup>show partiality.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13165L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13165L\"></sup>His majesty terrify you,And the dread of Him fall on you?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Your memorable sayings are proverbs of ashes,Your defenses are defenses of clay.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13167M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13167M\"></sup>Be silent before me so that I may speak;Then let come on me what may.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Why should I take my flesh in my teethAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13168N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13168N\"></sup>put my life in my hands?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13169O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13169O\"></sup>Though He slay me,I will hope in Him.Nevertheless I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13169P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13169P\"></sup>will argue my ways before Him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“This also will be my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13170Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13170Q\"></sup>salvation,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13170R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13170R\"></sup>a godless man may not come before His presence.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Listen carefully to my speech,And let my declaration <i>fill</i> your ears.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Behold now, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13172S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13172S\"></sup>prepared my case;I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13172T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13172T\"></sup>I will be vindicated.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13173U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13173U\"></sup>Who will contend with me?For then I would be silent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13173V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13173V\"></sup>die.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Only two things do not do to me,Then I will not hide from Your face:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13175W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13175W\"></sup>Remove Your hand from me,And let not the dread of You terrify me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Then call, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13176X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13176X\"></sup>I will answer;Or let me speak, then reply to me.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13177Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13177Y\"></sup>How many are my iniquities and sins?Make known to me my rebellion and my sin.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Why do You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13178Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13178Z\"></sup>hide Your faceAnd consider me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13178AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13178AA\"></sup>Your enemy?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Will You cause a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13179AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13179AB\"></sup>driven leaf to tremble?Or will You pursue the dry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13179AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13179AC\"></sup>chaff?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“For You write <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13180AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13180AD\"></sup>bitter things against meAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13180AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13180AE\"></sup>make me to inherit the iniquities of my youth.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13181AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13181AF\"></sup>put my feet in the stocksAnd watch all my paths;You set a limit for the soles of my feet,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>While I am decaying like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13182AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13182AG\"></sup>rotten thing,Like a garment that is moth-eaten."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13183A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13183A\"></sup>Man, who is born of woman,Is short-lived and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13183B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13183B\"></sup>full of turmoil.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13184C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13184C\"></sup>Like a flower he comes forth and withers.He also flees like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13184D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13184D\"></sup>a shadow and does not remain.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“You also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13185E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13185E\"></sup>open Your eyes on himAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13185F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13185F\"></sup>bring him into judgment with Yourself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13186G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13186G\"></sup>Who can make the clean out of the unclean?No one!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Since his days are determined,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13187H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13187H\"></sup>number of his months is with You;And his limits You have set so that he cannot pass.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13188I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13188I\"></sup>Turn Your gaze from him that he may rest,Until he fulfills his day like a hired man.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For there is hope for a tree,When it is cut down, that it will sprout again,And its shoots will not fail.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Though its roots grow old in the groundAnd its stump dies in the dry soil,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>At the scent of water it will flourishAnd put forth sprigs like a plant.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13192J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13192J\"></sup>man dies and lies prostrate.Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13192K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13192K\"></sup>expires, and where is he?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<i>As</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13193L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13193L\"></sup>water evaporates from the sea,And a river becomes parched and dried up,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13194M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13194M\"></sup>man lies down and does not rise.Until the heavens are no longer,He will not awake nor be aroused out of his sleep.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Oh that You would hide me in Sheol,That You would conceal me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13195N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13195N\"></sup>until Your wrath returns <i>to You</i>,That You would set a limit for me and remember me!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“If a man dies, will he live <i>again</i>?All the days of my struggle I will waitUntil my change comes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“You will call, and I will answer You;You will long for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13197O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13197O\"></sup>the work of Your hands.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For now You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13198P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13198P\"></sup>number my steps,You do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13198Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13198Q\"></sup>observe my sin.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“My transgression is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13199R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13199R\"></sup>sealed up in a bag,And You wrap up my iniquity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But the falling mountain crumbles away,And the rock moves from its place;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Water wears away stones,Its torrents wash away the dust of the earth;So You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13201S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13201S\"></sup>destroy man’s hope.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“You forever overpower him and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13202T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13202T\"></sup>departs;<i>You</i> change his appearance and send him away.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“His sons achieve honor, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13203U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13203U\"></sup>he does not know <i>it</i>;Or they become insignificant, but he does not perceive it.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“But his body pains him,And he mourns only for himself.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite responded,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Should a wise man answer with windy knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13206A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13206A\"></sup>And fill himself with the east wind?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Should he argue with useless talk,Or with words which are not profitable?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Indeed, you do away with reverenceAnd hinder meditation before God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13209B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13209B\"></sup>your guilt teaches your mouth,And you choose the language of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13209C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13209C\"></sup>the crafty.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13210D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13210D\"></sup>own mouth condemns you, and not I;And your own lips testify against you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Were you the first man to be born,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13211E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13211E\"></sup>were you brought forth before the hills?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Do you hear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13212F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13212F\"></sup>secret counsel of God,And limit wisdom to yourself?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13213G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13213G\"></sup>What do you know that we do not know?<i>What</i> do you understand that we do not?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Both the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13214H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13214H\"></sup>gray-haired and the aged are among us,Older than your father.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13215I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13215I\"></sup>the consolations of God too small for you,Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13215J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13215J\"></sup>word <i>spoken</i> gently with you?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Why does your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13216K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13216K\"></sup>heart carry you away?And why do your eyes flash,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>That you should turn your spirit against GodAnd allow <i>such</i> words to go out of your mouth?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“What is man, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13218L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13218L\"></sup>he should be pure,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13218M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13218M\"></sup>he who is born of a woman, that he should be righteous?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Behold, He puts no trust in His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13219N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13219N\"></sup>holy ones,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13219O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13219O\"></sup>heavens are not pure in His sight;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>How much less one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13220P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13220P\"></sup>detestable and corrupt,Man, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13220Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13220Q\"></sup>drinks iniquity like water!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I will tell you, listen to me;And what I have seen I will also declare;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>What wise men have told,And have not concealed from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13222R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13222R\"></sup>their fathers,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>To whom alone the land was given,And no alien passed among them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The wicked man writhes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13224S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13224S\"></sup>in pain all <i>his</i> days,And numbered are the years <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13224T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13224T\"></sup>stored up for the ruthless.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Sounds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13225U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13225U\"></sup>terror are in his ears;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13225V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13225V\"></sup>While at peace the destroyer comes upon him.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“He does not believe that he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13226W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13226W\"></sup>return from darkness,And he is destined for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13226X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13226X\"></sup>the sword.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“He wanders about for food, saying, ‘Where is it?’He knows that a day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13227Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13227Y\"></sup>darkness is at hand.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Distress and anguish terrify him,They overpower him like a king ready for the attack,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Because he has stretched out his hand against GodAnd conducts himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13229Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13229Z\"></sup>arrogantly against the Almighty.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“He rushes headlong at HimWith his massive shield.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“For he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13231AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13231AA\"></sup>covered his face with his fatAnd made his thighs heavy with flesh.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13232AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13232AB\"></sup>lived in desolate cities,In houses no one would inhabit,Which are destined to become ruins.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13233AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13233AC\"></sup>will not become rich, nor will his wealth endure;And his grain will not bend down to the ground.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13234AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13234AD\"></sup>not escape from darkness;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13234AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13234AE\"></sup>flame will wither his shoots,And by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13234AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13234AF\"></sup>the breath of His mouth he will go away.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Let him not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13235AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13235AG\"></sup>trust in emptiness, deceiving himself;For emptiness will be his reward.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“It will be accomplished <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13236AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13236AH\"></sup>before his time,And his palm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13236AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13236AI\"></sup>branch will not be green.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“He will drop off his unripe grape like the vine,And will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13237AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13237AJ\"></sup>cast off his flower like the olive tree.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“For the company of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13238AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13238AK\"></sup>the godless is barren,And fire consumes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13238AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13238AL\"></sup>the tents of the corrupt.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13239AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13239AM\"></sup>conceive mischief and bring forth iniquity,And their mind prepares deception.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then Job answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I have heard many such things;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13241A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13241A\"></sup>Sorry comforters are you all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Is there <i>no</i> limit to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13242B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13242B\"></sup>windy words?Or what plagues you that you answer?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I too could speak like you,If I were in your place.I could compose words against youAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13243C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13243C\"></sup>shake my head at you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I could strengthen you with my mouth,And the solace of my lips could lessen <i>your pain</i>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“If I speak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13245D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13245D\"></sup>my pain is not lessened,And if I hold back, what has left me?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But now He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13246E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13246E\"></sup>exhausted me;You have laid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13246F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13246F\"></sup>waste all my company.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“You have shriveled me up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13247G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13247G\"></sup>It has become a witness;And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13247H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13247H\"></sup>leanness rises up against me,It testifies to my face.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“His anger has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13248I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13248I\"></sup>torn me and hunted me down,He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13248J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13248J\"></sup>gnashed at me with His teeth;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13248K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13248K\"></sup>adversary glares at me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13249L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13249L\"></sup>gaped at me with their mouth,They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13249M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13249M\"></sup>slapped me on the cheek with contempt;They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13249N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13249N\"></sup>massed themselves against me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“God hands me over to ruffiansAnd tosses me into the hands of the wicked.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I was at ease, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13251O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13251O\"></sup>He shattered me,And He has grasped me by the neck and shaken me to pieces;He has also set me up as His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13251P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13251P\"></sup>target.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13252Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13252Q\"></sup>arrows surround me.Without mercy He splits my kidneys open;He pours out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13252R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13252R\"></sup>my gall on the ground.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13253S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13253S\"></sup>breaks through me with breach after breach;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13253T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13253T\"></sup>runs at me like a warrior.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I have sewed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13254U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13254U\"></sup>sackcloth over my skinAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13254V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13254V\"></sup>thrust my horn in the dust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“My face is flushed from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13255W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13255W\"></sup>weeping,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13255X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13255X\"></sup>And deep darkness is on my eyelids,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Although there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13256Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13256Y\"></sup>violence in my hands,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13256Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13256Z\"></sup>my prayer is pure.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“O earth, do not cover my blood,And let there be no <i>resting</i> place for my cry.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Even now, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13258AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13258AA\"></sup>my witness is in heaven,And my advocate is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13258AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13258AB\"></sup>on high.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“My friends are my scoffers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13259AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13259AC\"></sup>My eye weeps to God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“O that a man might plead with GodAs a man with his neighbor!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“For when a few years are past,I shall go the way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13261AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13261AD\"></sup>of no return."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>“My spirit is broken, my days are extinguished,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13262A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13262A\"></sup>grave is <i>ready</i> for me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13263B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13263B\"></sup>Surely mockers are with me,And my eye gazes on their provocation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Lay down, now, a pledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13264C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13264C\"></sup>for me with Yourself;Who is there that will be my guarantor?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13265D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13265D\"></sup>kept their heart from understanding,Therefore You will not exalt <i>them</i>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13266E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13266E\"></sup>informs against friends for a share <i>of the spoil</i>,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13266F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13266F\"></sup>eyes of his children also will languish.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“But He has made me a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13267G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13267G\"></sup>byword of the people,And I am one at whom men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13267H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13267H\"></sup>spit.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“My eye has also grown <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13268I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13268I\"></sup>dim because of grief,And all my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13268J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13268J\"></sup>members are as a shadow.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“The upright will be appalled at this,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13269K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13269K\"></sup>innocent will stir up himself against the godless.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Nevertheless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13270L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13270L\"></sup>the righteous will hold to his way,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13270M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13270M\"></sup>he who has clean hands will grow stronger and stronger.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But come again all of you now,For I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13271N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13271N\"></sup>do not find a wise man among you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13272O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13272O\"></sup>days are past, my plans are torn apart,<i>Even</i> the wishes of my heart.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“They make night into day, <i>saying</i>,‘The light is near,’ in the presence of darkness.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If I look for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13274P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13274P\"></sup>Sheol as my home,I make my bed in the darkness;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If I call to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13275Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13275Q\"></sup>pit, ‘You are my father’;To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13275R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13275R\"></sup>worm, ‘my mother and my sister’;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Where now is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13276S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13276S\"></sup>my hope?And who regards my hope?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Will it go down with me to Sheol?Shall we together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13277T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13277T\"></sup>go down into the dust?”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Then Bildad the Shuhite responded,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you hunt for words?Show understanding and then we can talk.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Why are we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13280A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13280A\"></sup>regarded as beasts,As stupid in your eyes?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“O you who tear yourself in your anger—For your sake is the earth to be abandoned,Or the rock to be moved from its place?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Indeed, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13282B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13282B\"></sup>light of the wicked goes out,And the flame of his fire gives no light.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“The light in his tent is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13283C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13283C\"></sup>darkened,And his lamp goes out above him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“His vigorous stride is shortened,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13284D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13284D\"></sup>own scheme brings him down.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13285E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13285E\"></sup>thrown into the net by his own feet,And he steps on the webbing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“A snare seizes <i>him</i> by the heel,<i>And</i> a trap snaps shut on him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“A noose for him is hidden in the ground,And a trap for him on the path.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“All around <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13288F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13288F\"></sup>terrors frighten him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13288G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13288G\"></sup>harry him at every step.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“His strength is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13289H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13289H\"></sup>famished,And calamity is ready at his side.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“His skin is devoured by disease,The firstborn of death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13290I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13290I\"></sup>devours his limbs.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13291J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13291J\"></sup>torn from the security of his tent,And they march him before the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13291K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13291K\"></sup>terrors.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“There dwells in his tent nothing of his;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13292L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13292L\"></sup>Brimstone is scattered on his habitation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13293M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13293M\"></sup>roots are dried below,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13293N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13293N\"></sup>branch is cut off above.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13294O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13294O\"></sup>Memory of him perishes from the earth,And he has no name abroad.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“He is driven from light <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13295P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13295P\"></sup>into darkness,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13295Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13295Q\"></sup>chased from the inhabited world.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He has no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13296R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13296R\"></sup>offspring or posterity among his people,Nor any survivor where he sojourned.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Those in the west are appalled at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13297S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13297S\"></sup>his fate,And those in the east are seized with horror.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Surely such are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13298T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13298T\"></sup>dwellings of the wicked,And this is the place of him who does not know God.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Then Job responded,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you torment meAnd crush me with words?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“These ten times you have insulted me;You are not ashamed to wrong me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Even if I have truly erred,My error lodges with me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If indeed you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13303A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13303A\"></sup>vaunt yourselves against meAnd prove my disgrace to me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Know then that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13304B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13304B\"></sup>God has wronged meAnd has closed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13304C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13304C\"></sup>His net around me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13305D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13305D\"></sup>I cry, ‘Violence!’ but I get no answer;I shout for help, but there is no justice.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13306E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13306E\"></sup>walled up my way so that I cannot pass,And He has put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13306F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13306F\"></sup>darkness on my paths.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13307G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13307G\"></sup>stripped my honor from meAnd removed the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13307H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13307H\"></sup>crown from my head.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13308I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13308I\"></sup>breaks me down on every side, and I am gone;And He has uprooted my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13308J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13308J\"></sup>hope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13308K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13308K\"></sup>like a tree.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“He has also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13309L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13309L\"></sup>kindled His anger against meAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13309M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13309M\"></sup>considered me as His enemy.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13310N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13310N\"></sup>troops come together,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13310O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13310O\"></sup>build up their way against meAnd camp around my tent.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13311P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13311P\"></sup>removed my brothers far from me,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13311Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13311Q\"></sup>acquaintances are completely estranged from me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“My relatives have failed,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13312R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13312R\"></sup>intimate friends have forgotten me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Those who live in my house and my maids consider me a stranger.I am a foreigner in their sight.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I call to my servant, but he does not answer;I have to implore him with my mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“My breath is offensive to my wife,And I am loathsome to my own brothers.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Even young children despise me;I rise up and they speak against me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“All my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13317S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13317S\"></sup>associates abhor me,And those I love have turned against me.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13318T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13318T\"></sup>bone clings to my skin and my flesh,And I have escaped <i>only</i> by the skin of my teeth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Pity me, pity me, O you my friends,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13319U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13319U\"></sup>hand of God has struck me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13320V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13320V\"></sup>persecute me as God <i>does</i>,And are not satisfied with my flesh?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Oh that my words were written!Oh that they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13321W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13321W\"></sup>inscribed in a book!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“That with an iron stylus and leadThey were engraved in the rock forever!",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“As for me, I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13323X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13323X\"></sup>my Redeemer lives,And at the last He will take His stand on the earth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Even after my skin is destroyed,Yet from my flesh I shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13324Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13324Y\"></sup>see God;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whom I myself shall behold,And whom my eyes will see and not another.My heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13325Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13325Z\"></sup>faints within me!",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“If you say, ‘How shall we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13326AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13326AA\"></sup>persecute him?’And ‘What pretext for a case against him can we find?’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“<i>Then</i> be afraid of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13327AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13327AB\"></sup>the sword for yourselves,For wrath <i>brings</i> the punishment of the sword,So that you may know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13327AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13327AC\"></sup>there is judgment.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Then Zophar the Naamathite answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Therefore my disquieting thoughts make me respond,Even because of my inward agitation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I listened to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13330A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13330A\"></sup>the reproof which insults me,And the spirit of my understanding makes me answer.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Do you know this from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13331B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13331B\"></sup>of old,From the establishment of man on earth,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>That the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13332C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13332C\"></sup>triumphing of the wicked is short,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13332D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13332D\"></sup>the joy of the godless momentary?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Though his loftiness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13333E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13333E\"></sup>reaches the heavens,And his head touches the clouds,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13334F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13334F\"></sup>perishes forever like his refuse;Those who have seen him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13334G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13334G\"></sup>will say, ‘Where is he?’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“He flies away like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13335H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13335H\"></sup>dream, and they cannot find him;Even like a vision of the night he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13335I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13335I\"></sup>chased away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13336J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13336J\"></sup>eye which saw him sees him no longer,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13336K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13336K\"></sup>his place no longer beholds him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13337L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13337L\"></sup>sons favor the poor,And his hands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13337M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13337M\"></sup>give back his wealth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13338N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13338N\"></sup>bones are full of his youthful vigor,But it lies down with him in the dust.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13339O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13339O\"></sup>evil is sweet in his mouth<i>And</i> he hides it under his tongue,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><i>Though</i> he desires it and will not let it go,But holds it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13340P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13340P\"></sup>in his mouth,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><i>Yet</i> his food in his stomach is changedTo the venom of cobras within him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“He swallows riches,But will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13342Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13342Q\"></sup>vomit them up;God will expel them from his belly.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“He sucks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13343R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13343R\"></sup>the poison of cobras;The viper’s tongue slays him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“He does not look at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13344S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13344S\"></sup>the streams,The rivers flowing with honey and curds.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13345T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13345T\"></sup>returns what he has attainedAnd cannot swallow <i>it</i>;As to the riches of his trading,He cannot even enjoy <i>them</i>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“For he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13346U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13346U\"></sup>oppressed <i>and</i> forsaken the poor;He has seized a house which he has not built.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Because he knew no quiet within him,He does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13347V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13347V\"></sup>not retain anything he desires.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Nothing remains for him to devour,Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13348W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13348W\"></sup>his prosperity does not endure.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“In the fullness of his plenty he will be cramped;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13349X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13349X\"></sup>hand of everyone who suffers will come <i>against</i> him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13350Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13350Y\"></sup>fills his belly,<i>God</i> will send His fierce anger on himAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13350Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13350Z\"></sup>rain <i>it</i> on him while he is eating.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“He may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13351AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13351AA\"></sup>flee from the iron weapon,<i>But</i> the bronze bow will pierce him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“It is drawn forth and comes out of his back,Even the glittering point from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13352AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13352AB\"></sup>his gall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13352AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13352AC\"></sup>Terrors come upon him,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Complete <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13353AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13353AD\"></sup>darkness is held in reserve for his treasures,And unfanned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13353AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13353AE\"></sup>fire will devour him;It will consume the survivor in his tent.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13354AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13354AF\"></sup>heavens will reveal his iniquity,And the earth will rise up against him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13355AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13355AG\"></sup>increase of his house will depart;<i>His possessions</i> will flow away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13355AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13355AH\"></sup>in the day of His anger.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“This is the wicked man’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13356AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13356AI\"></sup>portion from God,Even the heritage decreed to him by God.”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>Then Job answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Listen carefully to my speech,And let this be your <i>way of</i> consolation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Bear with me that I may speak;Then after I have spoken, you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13359A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13359A\"></sup>mock.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“As for me, is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13360B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13360B\"></sup>my complaint to man?And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13360C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13360C\"></sup>why should I not be impatient?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Look at me, and be astonished,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13361D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13361D\"></sup>put <i>your</i> hand over <i>your</i> mouth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Even when I remember, I am disturbed,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13362E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13362E\"></sup>horror takes hold of my flesh.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13363F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13363F\"></sup>do the wicked <i>still</i> live,Continue on, also become very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13363G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13363G\"></sup>powerful?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13364H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13364H\"></sup>descendants are established with them in their sight,And their offspring before their eyes,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their houses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13365I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13365I\"></sup>are safe from fear,And the rod of God is not on them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“His ox mates without fail;His cow calves and does not abort.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“They send forth their little ones like the flock,And their children skip about.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“They sing to the timbrel and harpAnd rejoice at the sound of the flute.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13369J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13369J\"></sup>spend their days in prosperity,And suddenly they go down to Sheol.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“They say to God, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13370K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13370K\"></sup>Depart from us!We do not even desire the knowledge of Your ways.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘Who is the Almighty, that we should serve Him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13371L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13371L\"></sup>what would we gain if we entreat Him?’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Behold, their prosperity is not in their hand;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13372M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13372M\"></sup>counsel of the wicked is far from me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“How often is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13373N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13373N\"></sup>the lamp of the wicked put out,Or does their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13373O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13373O\"></sup>calamity fall on them?Does God apportion destruction in His anger?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Are they as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13374P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13374P\"></sup>straw before the wind,And like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13374Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13374Q\"></sup>chaff which the storm carries away?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<i>You say</i>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13375R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13375R\"></sup>God stores away a man’s iniquity for his sons.’Let God repay him so that he may know <i>it</i>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Let his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13376S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13376S\"></sup>own eyes see his decay,And let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13376T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13376T\"></sup>drink of the wrath of the Almighty.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“For what does he care for his household after him,When the number of his months is cut off?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Can anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13378U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13378U\"></sup>teach God knowledge,In that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13378V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13378V\"></sup>judges those on high?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13379W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13379W\"></sup>dies in his full strength,Being wholly at ease and satisfied;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>His sides are filled out with fat,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13380X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13380X\"></sup>marrow of his bones is moist,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>While another dies with a bitter soul,Never even tasting <i>anything</i> good.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Together they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13382Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13382Y\"></sup>lie down in the dust,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13382Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13382Z\"></sup>worms cover them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Behold, I know your thoughts,And the plans by which you would wrong me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“For you say, ‘Where is the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13384AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13384AA\"></sup>the nobleman,And where is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13384AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13384AB\"></sup>tent, the dwelling places of the wicked?’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Have you not asked wayfaring men,And do you not recognize their witness?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13386AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13386AC\"></sup>wicked is reserved for the day of calamity;They will be led forth at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13386AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13386AD\"></sup>the day of fury.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Who will confront him with his actions,And who will repay him for what he has done?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“While he is carried to the grave,<i>Men</i> will keep watch over <i>his</i> tomb.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13389AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13389AE\"></sup>clods of the valley will gently cover him;Moreover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13389AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13389AF\"></sup>all men will follow after him,While countless ones <i>go</i> before him.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“How then will you vainly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13390AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13390AG\"></sup>comfort me,For your answers remain <i>full of</i> falsehood?”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite responded,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Can a vigorous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13392A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13392A\"></sup>man be of use to God,Or a wise man be useful to himself?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Is there any pleasure to the Almighty if you are righteous,Or profit if you make your ways perfect?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Is it because of your reverence that He reproves you,That He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13394B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13394B\"></sup>enters into judgment against you?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13395C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13395C\"></sup>your wickedness great,And your iniquities without end?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13396D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13396D\"></sup>taken pledges of your brothers without cause,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13396E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13396E\"></sup>stripped men naked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“To the weary you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13397F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13397F\"></sup>given no water to drink,And from the hungry you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13397G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13397G\"></sup>withheld bread.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13398H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13398H\"></sup>belongs to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13398I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13398I\"></sup>mighty man,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13398J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13398J\"></sup>the honorable man dwells in it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“You have sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13399K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13399K\"></sup>widows away empty,And the strength of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13399L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13399L\"></sup>orphans has been crushed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13400M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13400M\"></sup>snares surround you,And sudden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13400N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13400N\"></sup>dread terrifies you,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13401O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13401O\"></sup>darkness, so that you cannot see,And an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13401P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13401P\"></sup>abundance of water covers you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Is not God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13402Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13402Q\"></sup><i>in</i> the height of heaven?Look also at the distant stars, how high they are!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“You say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13403R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13403R\"></sup>What does God know?Can He judge through the thick darkness?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13404S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13404S\"></sup>Clouds are a hiding place for Him, so that He cannot see;And He walks on the vault of heaven.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Will you keep to the ancient pathWhich <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13405T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13405T\"></sup>wicked men have trod,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Who were snatched away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13406U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13406U\"></sup>before their time,Whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13406V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13406V\"></sup>foundations were washed away by a river?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13407W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13407W\"></sup>said to God, ‘Depart from us!’And ‘What can the Almighty do to them?’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Yet He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13408X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13408X\"></sup>filled their houses with good <i>things</i>;But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13408Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13408Y\"></sup>the counsel of the wicked is far from me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13409Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13409Z\"></sup>righteous see and are glad,And the innocent mock them,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><i>Saying</i>, ‘Truly our adversaries are cut off,And their abundance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13410AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13410AA\"></sup>the fire has consumed.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13411AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13411AB\"></sup>Yield now and be at peace with Him;Thereby good will come to you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Please receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13412AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13412AC\"></sup>instruction from His mouthAnd establish His words in your heart.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13413AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13413AD\"></sup>return to the Almighty, you will be restored;If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13413AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13413AE\"></sup>remove unrighteousness far from your tent,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13414AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13414AF\"></sup>place <i>your</i> gold in the dust,And <i>the gold of</i> Ophir among the stones of the brooks,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then the Almighty will be your goldAnd choice silver to you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“For then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13416AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13416AG\"></sup>delight in the AlmightyAnd lift up your face to God.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13417AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13417AH\"></sup>pray to Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13417AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13417AI\"></sup>He will hear you;And you will pay your vows.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“You will also decree a thing, and it will be established for you;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13418AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13418AJ\"></sup>light will shine on your ways.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“When you are cast down, you will speak with confidence,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13419AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13419AK\"></sup>humble person He will save.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“He will deliver one who is not innocent,And he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13420AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13420AL\"></sup>delivered through the cleanness of your hands.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>Then Job replied,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Even today my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13422A\"></sup>complaint is rebellion;His hand is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13422B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13422B\"></sup>heavy despite my groaning.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Oh that I knew where I might find Him,That I might come to His seat!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13424C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13424C\"></sup>present <i>my</i> case before HimAnd fill my mouth with arguments.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I would learn the words <i>which</i> He would answer,And perceive what He would say to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Would He contend with me by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13426D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13426D\"></sup>the greatness of <i>His</i> power?No, surely He would pay attention to me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“There the upright would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13427E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13427E\"></sup>reason with Him;And I would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13427F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13427F\"></sup>delivered forever from my Judge.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Behold, I go forward but He is not <i>there</i>,And backward, but I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13428G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13428G\"></sup>cannot perceive Him;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When He acts on the left, I cannot behold <i>Him</i>;He turns on the right, I cannot see Him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But He knows the way I take;<i>When</i> He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13430H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13430H\"></sup>tried me, I shall come forth as gold.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“My foot has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13431I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13431I\"></sup>held fast to His path;I have kept His way and not turned aside.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I have not departed from the command of His lips;I have treasured the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13432J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13432J\"></sup>words of His mouth more than my necessary food.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“But He is unique and who can turn Him?And <i>what</i> His soul desires, that He does.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“For He performs what is appointed for me,And many such <i>decrees</i> are with Him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Therefore, I would be dismayed at His presence;<i>When</i> I consider, I am terrified of Him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<i>It is</i> God <i>who</i> has made my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13436K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13436K\"></sup>heart faint,And the Almighty <i>who</i> has dismayed me,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13437L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13437L\"></sup>am not silenced by the darkness,Nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13437M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13437M\"></sup>deep gloom <i>which</i> covers me."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13438A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13438A\"></sup>Why are times not stored up by the Almighty,And why do those who know Him not see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13438B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13438B\"></sup>His days?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13439C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13439C\"></sup>remove the landmarks;They seize and devour flocks.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“They drive away the donkeys of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13440D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13440D\"></sup>orphans;They take the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13440E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13440E\"></sup>widow’s ox for a pledge.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“They push <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13441F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13441F\"></sup>the needy aside from the road;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13441G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13441G\"></sup>poor of the land are made to hide themselves altogether.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Behold, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13442H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13442H\"></sup>wild donkeys in the wildernessThey <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13442I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13442I\"></sup>go forth seeking food in their activity,As bread for <i>their</i> children in the desert.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“They harvest their fodder in the fieldAnd glean the vineyard of the wicked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13444J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13444J\"></sup>They spend the night naked, without clothing,And have no covering against the cold.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“They are wet with the mountain rainsAnd hug the rock for want of a shelter.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Others snatch the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13446K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13446K\"></sup>orphan from the breast,And against the poor they take a pledge.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They cause <i>the poor</i> to go about naked without clothing,And they take away the sheaves from the hungry.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Within the walls they produce oil;They tread wine presses but thirst.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“From the city men groan,And the souls of the wounded cry out;Yet God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13449L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13449L\"></sup>does not pay attention to folly.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Others have been with those who rebel against the light;They do not want to know its waysNor abide in its paths.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“The murderer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13451M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13451M\"></sup>arises at dawn;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13451N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13451N\"></sup>kills the poor and the needy,And at night he is as a thief.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The eye of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13452O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13452O\"></sup>adulterer waits for the twilight,Saying, ‘No eye will see me.’And he disguises his face.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“In the dark they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13453P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13453P\"></sup>dig into houses,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13453Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13453Q\"></sup>shut themselves up by day;They do not know the light.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For the morning is the same to him as thick darkness,For he is familiar with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13454R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13454R\"></sup>terrors of thick darkness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13455S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13455S\"></sup>insignificant on the surface of the water;Their portion is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13455T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13455T\"></sup>cursed on the earth.They do not turn toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13455U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13455U\"></sup>vineyards.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Drought and heat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13456V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13456V\"></sup>consume the snow waters,<i>So does</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13456W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13456W\"></sup>Sheol <i>those who</i> have sinned.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13457X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13457X\"></sup>mother will forget him;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13457Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13457Y\"></sup>worm feeds sweetly till he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13457Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13457Z\"></sup>no longer remembered.And wickedness will be broken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13457AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13457AA\"></sup>like a tree.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“He wrongs the barren womanAnd does no good for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13458AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13458AB\"></sup>the widow.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“But He drags off the valiant by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13459AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13459AC\"></sup>His power;He rises, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13459AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13459AD\"></sup>no one has assurance of life.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“He provides them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13460AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13460AE\"></sup>with security, and they are supported;And His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13460AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13460AF\"></sup>eyes are on their ways.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“They are exalted a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13461AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13461AG\"></sup>little while, then they are gone;Moreover, they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13461AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13461AH\"></sup>brought low and like everything gathered up;Even like the heads of grain they are cut off.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Now if it is not so, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13462AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13462AI\"></sup>who can prove me a liar,And make my speech worthless?”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>Then Bildad the Shuhite answered,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13464A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13464A\"></sup>Dominion and awe belong to HimWho establishes peace in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13464B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13464B\"></sup>His heights.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Is there any number to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13465C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13465C\"></sup>His troops?And upon whom does His light not rise?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“How then can a man be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13466D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13466D\"></sup>just with God?Or how can he be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13466E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13466E\"></sup>clean who is born of woman?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13467F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13467F\"></sup>the moon has no brightnessAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13467G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13467G\"></sup>stars are not pure in His sight,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>How much less <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13468H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13468H\"></sup>man, <i>that</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13468I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13468I\"></sup>maggot,And the son of man, <i>that</i> worm!”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Then Job responded,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“What a help you are to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13470A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13470A\"></sup>the weak!How you have saved the arm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13470B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13470B\"></sup>without strength!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“What counsel you have given to <i>one</i> without wisdom!What helpful insight you have abundantly provided!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“To whom have you uttered words?And whose spirit was expressed through you?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13473C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13473C\"></sup>departed spirits trembleUnder the waters and their inhabitants.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Naked is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13474D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13474D\"></sup>Sheol before Him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13474E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13474E\"></sup>Abaddon has no covering.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13475F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13475F\"></sup>stretches out the north over empty spaceAnd hangs the earth on nothing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13476G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13476G\"></sup>wraps up the waters in His clouds,And the cloud does not burst under them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13477H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13477H\"></sup>obscures the face of the full moonAnd spreads His cloud over it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He has inscribed a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13478I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13478I\"></sup>circle on the surface of the watersAt the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13478J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13478J\"></sup>boundary of light and darkness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“The pillars of heaven trembleAnd are amazed at His rebuke.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13480K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13480K\"></sup>quieted the sea with His power,And by His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13480L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13480L\"></sup>understanding He shattered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13480M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13480M\"></sup>Rahab.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“By His breath the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13481N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13481N\"></sup>heavens are cleared;His hand has pierced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13481O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13481O\"></sup>the fleeing serpent.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Behold, these are the fringes of His ways;And how faint <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13482P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13482P\"></sup>a word we hear of Him!But His mighty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13482Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13482Q\"></sup>thunder, who can understand?”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>Then Job continued his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13483A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13483A\"></sup>discourse and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“As God lives, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13484B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13484B\"></sup>who has taken away my right,And the Almighty, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13484C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13484C\"></sup>who has embittered my soul,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For as long as life is in me,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13485D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13485D\"></sup>breath of God is in my nostrils,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My lips certainly will not speak unjustly,Nor will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13486E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13486E\"></sup>my tongue mutter deceit.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Far be it from me that I should declare you right;Till I die <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13487F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13487F\"></sup>I will not put away my integrity from me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13488G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13488G\"></sup>hold fast my righteousness and will not let it go.My heart does not reproach any of my days.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“May my enemy be as the wickedAnd my opponent as the unjust.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13490H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13490H\"></sup>the hope of the godless when he is cut off,When God requires <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13490I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13490I\"></sup>his life?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Will God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13491J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13491J\"></sup>hear his cryWhen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13491K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13491K\"></sup>distress comes upon him?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Will he take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13492L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13492L\"></sup>delight in the Almighty?Will he call on God at all times?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will instruct you in the power of God;What is with the Almighty I will not conceal.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Behold, all of you have seen <i>it</i>;Why then do you act foolishly?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13495M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13495M\"></sup>the portion of a wicked man from God,And the inheritance <i>which</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13495N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13495N\"></sup>tyrants receive from the Almighty.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Though his sons are many, they are destined <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13496O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13496O\"></sup>for the sword;And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13496P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13496P\"></sup>descendants will not be satisfied with bread.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“His survivors will be buried because of the plague,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13497Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13497Q\"></sup>widows will not be able to weep.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Though he piles up silver like dustAnd prepares garments as <i>plentiful as</i> the clay,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He may prepare <i>it</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13499R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13499R\"></sup>but the just will wear <i>it</i>And the innocent will divide the silver.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“He has built his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13500S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13500S\"></sup>house like the spider’s web,Or as a hut <i>which</i> the watchman has made.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He lies down rich, but never again;He opens his eyes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13501T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13501T\"></sup>it is no longer.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13502U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13502U\"></sup>Terrors overtake him like a flood;A tempest steals him away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13502V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13502V\"></sup>in the night.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“The east <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13503W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13503W\"></sup>wind carries him away, and he is gone,For it whirls him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13503X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13503X\"></sup>away from his place.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“For it will hurl at him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13504Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13504Y\"></sup>without sparing;He will surely try to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13504Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13504Z\"></sup>flee from its power.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<i>Men</i> will clap their hands at himAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13505AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13505AA\"></sup>hiss him from his place."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>“Surely there is a mine for silverAnd a place where they refine gold.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Iron is taken from the dust,And copper is smelted from rock.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<i>Man</i> puts an end to darkness,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13508A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13508A\"></sup>to the farthest limit he searches outThe rock in gloom and deep shadow.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“He sinks a shaft far from habitation,Forgotten by the foot;They hang and swing to and fro far from men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“The earth, from it comes food,And underneath it is turned up as fire.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Its rocks are the source of sapphires,And its dust <i>contains</i> gold.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“The path no bird of prey knows,Nor has the falcon’s eye caught sight of it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“The proud beasts have not trodden it,Nor has the <i>fierce</i> lion passed over it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“He puts his hand on the flint;He overturns the mountains at the base.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He hews out channels through the rocks,And his eye sees anything precious.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“He dams up the streams from flowing,And what is hidden he brings out to the light.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13517B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13517B\"></sup>where can wisdom be found?And where is the place of understanding?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13518C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13518C\"></sup>Man does not know its value,Nor is it found in the land of the living.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“The deep says, ‘It is not in me’;And the sea says, ‘It is not with me.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13520D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13520D\"></sup>Pure gold cannot be given in exchange for it,Nor can silver be weighed as its price.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“It cannot be valued in the gold of Ophir,In precious onyx, or sapphire.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13522E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13522E\"></sup>Gold or glass cannot equal it,Nor can it be exchanged for articles of fine gold.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Coral and crystal are not to be mentioned;And the acquisition of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13523F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13523F\"></sup>wisdom is above <i>that of</i> pearls.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“The topaz of Ethiopia cannot equal it,Nor can it be valued in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13524G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13524G\"></sup>pure gold.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13525H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13525H\"></sup>Where then does wisdom come from?And where is the place of understanding?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Thus it is hidden from the eyes of all livingAnd concealed from the birds of the sky.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13527I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13527I\"></sup>Abaddon and Death say,‘With our ears we have heard a report of it.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13528J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13528J\"></sup>God understands its way,And He knows its place.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“For He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13529K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13529K\"></sup>looks to the ends of the earthAnd sees everything under the heavens.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“When He imparted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13530L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13530L\"></sup>weight to the windAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13530M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13530M\"></sup>meted out the waters by measure,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When He set a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13531N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13531N\"></sup>limit for the rainAnd a course for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13531O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13531O\"></sup>thunderbolt,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then He saw it and declared it;He established it and also searched it out.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And to man He said, ‘Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13533P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13533P\"></sup>fear of the Lord, that is wisdom;And to depart from evil is understanding.’”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>And Job again took up his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13534A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13534A\"></sup>discourse and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Oh that I were as in months gone by,As in the days when God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13535B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13535B\"></sup>watched over me;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13536C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13536C\"></sup>His lamp shone over my head,<i>And</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13536D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13536D\"></sup>by His light I walked through darkness;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As I was in the prime of my days,When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13537E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13537E\"></sup>friendship of God <i>was</i> over my tent;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the Almighty was yet with me,<i>And</i> my children were around me;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When my steps were bathed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13539F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13539F\"></sup>butter,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13539G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13539G\"></sup>rock poured out for me streams of oil!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“When I went out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13540H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13540H\"></sup>the gate of the city,When I took my seat in the square,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The young men saw me and hid themselves,And the old men arose <i>and</i> stood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The princes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13542I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13542I\"></sup>stopped talkingAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13542J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13542J\"></sup>put <i>their</i> hands on their mouths;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The voice of the nobles was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13543K\"></sup>hushed,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13543L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13543L\"></sup>tongue stuck to their palate.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13544M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13544M\"></sup>the ear heard, it called me blessed,And when the eye saw, it gave witness of me,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Because I delivered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13545N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13545N\"></sup>the poor who cried for help,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13545O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13545O\"></sup>orphan who had no helper.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The blessing of the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13546P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13546P\"></sup>ready to perish came upon me,And I made the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13546Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13546Q\"></sup>widow’s heart sing for joy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13547R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13547R\"></sup>put on righteousness, and it clothed me;My justice was like a robe and a turban.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13548S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13548S\"></sup>eyes to the blindAnd feet to the lame.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I was a father to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13549T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13549T\"></sup>the needy,And I investigated the case which I did not know.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13550U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13550U\"></sup>broke the jaws of the wickedAnd snatched the prey from his teeth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Then I thought, ‘I shall die in my nest,And I shall multiply <i>my</i> days as the sand.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13552V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13552V\"></sup>root is spread out to the waters,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13552W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13552W\"></sup>dew lies all night on my branch.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>‘My glory is <i>ever</i> new with me,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13553X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13553X\"></sup>bow is renewed in my hand.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“To me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13554Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13554Y\"></sup>they listened and waited,And kept silent for my counsel.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“After my words they did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13555Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13555Z\"></sup>speak again,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13555AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13555AA\"></sup>my speech dropped on them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“They waited for me as for the rain,And opened their mouth as for the spring rain.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“I smiled on them when they did not believe,And the light of my face they did not cast down.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I chose a way for them and sat as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13558AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13558AB\"></sup>chief,And dwelt as a king among the troops,As one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13558AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13558AC\"></sup>comforted the mourners."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>“But now those younger than I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13559A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13559A\"></sup>mock me,Whose fathers I disdained to put with the dogs of my flock.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Indeed, what <i>good was</i> the strength of their hands to me?Vigor had perished from them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“From want and famine they are gauntWho gnaw the dry ground by night in waste and desolation,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who pluck mallow by the bushes,And whose food is the root of the broom shrub.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“They are driven from the community;They shout against them as <i>against</i> a thief,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So that they dwell in dreadful valleys,In holes of the earth and of the rocks.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Among the bushes they cry out;Under the nettles they are gathered together.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Fools, even those without a name,They were scourged from the land.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And now I have become their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13567B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13567B\"></sup>taunt,I have even become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13567C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13567C\"></sup>byword to them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They abhor me <i>and</i> stand aloof from me,And they do not refrain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13568D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13568D\"></sup>spitting at my face.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Because He has loosed His bowstring and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13569E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13569E\"></sup>afflicted me,They have cast off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13569F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13569F\"></sup>the bridle before me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“On the right hand their brood arises;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13570G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13570G\"></sup>thrust aside my feet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13570H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13570H\"></sup>and build up against me their ways of destruction.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13571I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13571I\"></sup>break up my path,They profit from my destruction;No one restrains them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“As <i>through</i> a wide breach they come,Amid the tempest they roll on.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13573J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13573J\"></sup>Terrors are turned against me;They pursue my honor as the wind,And my prosperity has passed away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13573K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13573K\"></sup>like a cloud.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“And now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13574L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13574L\"></sup>my soul is poured out within me;Days of affliction have seized me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“At night it pierces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13575M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13575M\"></sup>my bones within me,And my gnawing <i>pains</i> take no rest.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“By a great force my garment is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13576N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13576N\"></sup>distorted;It binds me about as the collar of my coat.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He has cast me into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13577O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13577O\"></sup>mire,And I have become like dust and ashes.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13578P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13578P\"></sup>cry out to You for help, but You do not answer me;I stand up, and You turn Your attention against me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“You have become cruel to me;With the might of Your hand You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13579Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13579Q\"></sup>persecute me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13580R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13580R\"></sup>lift me up to the wind <i>and</i> cause me to ride;And You dissolve me in a storm.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“For I know that You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13581S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13581S\"></sup>will bring me to deathAnd to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13581T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13581T\"></sup>house of meeting for all living.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Yet does not one in a heap of ruins stretch out <i>his</i> hand,Or in his disaster therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13582U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13582U\"></sup>cry out for help?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Have I not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13583V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13583V\"></sup>wept for the one whose life is hard?Was not my soul grieved for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13583W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13583W\"></sup>the needy?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13584X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13584X\"></sup>expected good, then evil came;When I waited for light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13584Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13584Y\"></sup>then darkness came.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I am seething <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13585Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13585Z\"></sup>within and cannot relax;Days of affliction confront me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“I go about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13586AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13586AA\"></sup>mourning without comfort;I stand up in the assembly <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13586AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13586AB\"></sup>cry out for help.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“I have become a brother to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13587AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13587AC\"></sup>jackalsAnd a companion of ostriches.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13588AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13588AD\"></sup>skin turns black on me,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13588AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13588AE\"></sup>bones burn with fever.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Therefore my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13589AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13589AF\"></sup>harp is turned to mourning,And my flute to the sound of those who weep."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>“I have made a covenant with my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13590A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13590A\"></sup>eyes;How then could I gaze at a virgin?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13591B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13591B\"></sup>the portion of God from aboveOr the heritage of the Almighty from on high?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Is it not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13592C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13592C\"></sup>calamity to the unjustAnd disaster to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13592D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13592D\"></sup>those who work iniquity?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Does He not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13593E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13593E\"></sup>see my waysAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13593F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13593F\"></sup>number all my steps?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13594G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13594G\"></sup>walked with falsehood,And my foot has hastened after deceit,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Let Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13595H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13595H\"></sup>weigh me with accurate scales,And let God know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13595I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13595I\"></sup>my integrity.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“If my step has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13596J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13596J\"></sup>turned from the way,Or my heart followed my eyes,Or if any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13596K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13596K\"></sup>spot has stuck to my hands,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Let me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13597L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13597L\"></sup>sow and another eat,And let my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13597M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13597M\"></sup>crops be uprooted.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“If my heart has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13598N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13598N\"></sup>enticed by a woman,Or I have lurked at my neighbor’s doorway,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>May my wife <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13599O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13599O\"></sup>grind for another,And let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13599P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13599P\"></sup>others kneel down over her.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For that would be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13600Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13600Q\"></sup>lustful crime;Moreover, it would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13600R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13600R\"></sup>an iniquity <i>punishable by</i> judges.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“For it would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13601S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13601S\"></sup>fire that consumes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13601T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13601T\"></sup>Abaddon,And would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13601U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13601U\"></sup>uproot all my increase.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13602V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13602V\"></sup>despised the claim of my male or female slavesWhen they filed a complaint against me,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>What then could I do when God arises?And when He calls me to account, what will I answer Him?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13604W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13604W\"></sup>He who made me in the womb make him,And the same one fashion us in the womb?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“If I have kept <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13605X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13605X\"></sup>the poor from <i>their</i> desire,Or have caused the eyes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13605Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13605Y\"></sup>the widow to fail,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Or have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13606Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13606Z\"></sup>eaten my morsel alone,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13606AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13606AA\"></sup>the orphan has not shared it",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>(But from my youth he grew up with me as with a father,And from infancy I guided her),",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If I have seen anyone perish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13608AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13608AB\"></sup>for lack of clothing,Or that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13608AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13608AC\"></sup>the needy had no covering,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If his loins have not thanked me,And if he has not been warmed with the fleece of my sheep,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>If I have lifted up my hand against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13610AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13610AD\"></sup>the orphan,Because I saw I had support <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13610AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13610AE\"></sup>in the gate,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Let my shoulder fall from the socket,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13611AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13611AF\"></sup>arm be broken off at the elbow.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13612AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13612AG\"></sup>calamity from God is a terror to me,And because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13612AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13612AH\"></sup>His majesty I can do nothing.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“If I have put my confidence <i>in</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13613AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13613AI\"></sup>gold,And called fine gold my trust,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13614AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13614AJ\"></sup>gloated because my wealth was great,And because my hand had secured <i>so</i> much;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13615AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13615AK\"></sup>looked at the sun when it shoneOr the moon going in splendor,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And my heart became secretly enticed,And my hand threw a kiss from my mouth,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>That too would have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13617AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13617AL\"></sup>an iniquity <i>calling for</i> judgment,For I would have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13617AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13617AM\"></sup>denied God above.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Have I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13618AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13618AN\"></sup>rejoiced at the extinction of my enemy,Or exulted when evil befell him?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13619AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13619AO\"></sup>I have not allowed my mouth to sinBy asking for his life in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13619AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13619AP\"></sup>a curse.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Have the men of my tent not said,‘Who can find one who has not been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13620AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13620AQ\"></sup>satisfied with his meat’?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“The alien has not lodged outside,<i>For</i> I have opened my doors to the traveler.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Have I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13622AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13622AR\"></sup>covered my transgressions like Adam,By hiding my iniquity in my bosom,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Because I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13623AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13623AS\"></sup>feared the great multitude,And the contempt of families terrified me,And kept silent and did not go out of doors?",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“Oh that I had one to hear me!Behold, here is my signature;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13624AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13624AT\"></sup>Let the Almighty answer me!And the indictment which my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13624AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13624AU\"></sup>adversary has written,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Surely I would carry it on my shoulder,I would bind it to myself like a crown.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“I would declare to Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13626AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13626AV\"></sup>the number of my steps;Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13626AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13626AW\"></sup>a prince I would approach Him.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“If my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13627AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13627AX\"></sup>land cries out against me,And its furrows weep together;",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13628AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13628AY\"></sup>eaten its fruit without money,Or have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13628AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13628AZ\"></sup>caused its owners to lose their lives,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13629BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13629BA\"></sup>briars grow instead of wheat,And stinkweed instead of barley.”The words of Job are ended."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>Then these three men ceased answering Job, because he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13630A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13630A\"></sup>righteous in his own eyes.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But the anger of Elihu the son of Barachel the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13631B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13631B\"></sup>Buzite, of the family of Ram burned; against Job his anger burned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13631C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13631C\"></sup>because he justified himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13631D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13631D\"></sup>before God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And his anger burned against his three friends because they had found no answer, and yet had condemned Job.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now Elihu had waited to speak to Job because they were years older than he.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when Elihu saw that there was no answer in the mouth of the three men his anger burned.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So Elihu the son of Barachel the Buzite spoke out and said,“I am young in years and you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13635E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13635E\"></sup>old;Therefore I was shy and afraid to tell you what I think.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I thought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13636F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13636F\"></sup>age should speak,And increased years should teach wisdom.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But it is a spirit in man,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13637G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13637G\"></sup>breath of the Almighty gives them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13637H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13637H\"></sup>understanding.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The abundant <i>in years</i> may not be wise,Nor may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13638I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13638I\"></sup>elders understand justice.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“So I say, ‘Listen to me,I too will tell what I think.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Behold, I waited for your words,I listened to your reasonings,While you pondered what to say.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I even paid close attention to you;Indeed, there was no one who refuted Job,Not one of you who answered his words.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Do not say,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13642J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13642J\"></sup>We have found wisdom;God will rout him, not man.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“For he has not arranged <i>his</i> words against me,Nor will I reply to him with your arguments.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“They are dismayed, they no longer answer;Words have failed them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Shall I wait, because they do not speak,Because they stop <i>and</i> no longer answer?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I too will answer my share,I also will tell my opinion.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“For I am full of words;The spirit within me constrains me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Behold, my belly is like unvented wine,Like new wineskins it is about to burst.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Let me speak that I may get relief;Let me open my lips and answer.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Let me now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13650K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13650K\"></sup>be partial to no one,Nor flatter <i>any</i> man.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“For I do not know how to flatter,<i>Else</i> my Maker would soon take me away."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>“However now, Job, please <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13652A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13652A\"></sup>hear my speech,And listen to all my words.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Behold now, I open my mouth,My tongue in my mouth speaks.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“My words are <i>from</i> the uprightness of my heart,And my lips speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13654B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13654B\"></sup>knowledge sincerely.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13655C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13655C\"></sup>Spirit of God has made me,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13655D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13655D\"></sup>breath of the Almighty gives me life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13656E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13656E\"></sup>Refute me if you can;Array yourselves before me, take your stand.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Behold, I belong to God like you;I too have been formed out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13657F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13657F\"></sup>clay.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13658G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13658G\"></sup>no fear of me should terrify you,Nor should my pressure weigh heavily on you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Surely you have spoken in my hearing,And I have heard the sound of <i>your</i> words:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13660H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13660H\"></sup>pure, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13660I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13660I\"></sup>without transgression;I am innocent and there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13660J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13660J\"></sup>is no guilt in me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Behold, He invents pretexts against me;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13661K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13661K\"></sup>counts me as His enemy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13662L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13662L\"></sup>puts my feet in the stocks;He watches all my paths.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Behold, let me tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13663M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13663M\"></sup>you are not right in this,For God is greater than man.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13664N\"></sup>complain against HimThat He does not give an account of all His doings?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13665O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13665O\"></sup>God speaks once,Or twice, <i>yet</i> no one notices it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“In a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13666P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13666P\"></sup>dream, a vision of the night,When sound sleep falls on men,While they slumber in their beds,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13667Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13667Q\"></sup>He opens the ears of men,And seals their instruction,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>That He may turn man aside <i>from his</i> conduct,And keep man from pride;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13669R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13669R\"></sup>keeps back his soul from the pit,And his life from passing over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13669S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13669S\"></sup>into Sheol.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Man is also chastened with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13670T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13670T\"></sup>pain on his bed,And with unceasing complaint in his bones;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So that his life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13671U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13671U\"></sup>loathes bread,And his soul favorite food.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13672V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13672V\"></sup>flesh wastes away from sight,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13672W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13672W\"></sup>bones which were not seen stick out.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13673X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13673X\"></sup>his soul draws near to the pit,And his life to those who bring death.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“If there is an angel <i>as</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13674Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13674Y\"></sup>mediator for him,One out of a thousand,To remind a man what is right for him,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then let him be gracious to him, and say,‘Deliver him from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13675Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13675Z\"></sup>going down to the pit,I have found a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13675AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13675AA\"></sup>ransom’;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let his flesh become fresher than in youth,Let him return to the days of his youthful vigor;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13677AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13677AB\"></sup>pray to God, and He will accept him,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13677AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13677AC\"></sup>he may see His face with joy,And He may restore His righteousness to man.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“He will sing to men and say,‘I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13678AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13678AD\"></sup>have sinned and perverted what is right,And it is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13678AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13678AE\"></sup>proper for me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>‘He has redeemed my soul from going to the pit,And my life shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13679AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13679AF\"></sup>see the light.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Behold, God does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13680AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13680AG\"></sup>all these oftentimes with men,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13681AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13681AH\"></sup>bring back his soul from the pit,That he may be enlightened with the light of life.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Pay attention, O Job, listen to me;Keep silent, and let me speak.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“<i>Then</i> if you have anything to say, answer me;Speak, for I desire to justify you.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“If not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13684AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13684AI\"></sup>listen to me;Keep silent, and I will teach you wisdom.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Then Elihu continued and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Hear my words, you wise men,And listen to me, you who know.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13687A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13687A\"></sup>the ear tests wordsAs the palate tastes food.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Let us choose for ourselves what is right;Let us know among ourselves what is good.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For Job has said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13689B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13689B\"></sup>I am righteous,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13689C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13689C\"></sup>God has taken away my right;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Should I lie concerning my right?My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13690D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13690D\"></sup>wound is incurable, <i>though I am</i> without transgression.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“What man is like Job,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13691E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13691E\"></sup>drinks up derision like water,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who goes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13692F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13692F\"></sup>in company with the workers of iniquity,And walks with wicked men?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For he has said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13693G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13693G\"></sup>It profits a man nothingWhen he is pleased with God.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Therefore, listen to me, you men of understanding.Far be it from God to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13694H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13694H\"></sup>do wickedness,And from the Almighty to do wrong.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For He pays a man according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13695I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13695I\"></sup>his work,And makes him find it according to his way.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Surely, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13696J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13696J\"></sup>God will not act wickedly,And the Almighty will not pervert justice.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13697K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13697K\"></sup>gave Him authority over the earth?And who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13697L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13697L\"></sup>has laid <i>on Him</i> the whole world?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“If He should determine to do so,If He should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13698M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13698M\"></sup>gather to Himself His spirit and His breath,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13699N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13699N\"></sup>flesh would perish together,And man would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13699O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13699O\"></sup>return to dust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“But if <i>you have</i> understanding, hear this;Listen to the sound of my words.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13701P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13701P\"></sup>one who hates justice rule?And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13701Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13701Q\"></sup>will you condemn the righteous mighty One,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Who says to a king, ‘Worthless one,’To nobles, ‘Wicked ones’;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Who shows no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13703R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13703R\"></sup>partiality to princesNor regards the rich above the poor,For they all are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13703S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13703S\"></sup>work of His hands?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“In a moment they die, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13704T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13704T\"></sup>at midnightPeople are shaken and pass away,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13704U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13704U\"></sup>the mighty are taken away without a hand.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13705V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13705V\"></sup>His eyes are upon the ways of a man,And He sees all his steps.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13706W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13706W\"></sup>no darkness or deep shadowWhere the workers of iniquity may hide themselves.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“For He does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13707X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13707X\"></sup><i>need to</i> consider a man further,That he should go before God in judgment.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“He breaks in pieces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13708Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13708Y\"></sup>mighty men without inquiry,And sets others in their place.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Therefore He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13709Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13709Z\"></sup>knows their works,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13709AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13709AA\"></sup>He overthrows <i>them</i> in the night,And they are crushed.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13710AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13710AB\"></sup>strikes them like the wickedIn a public place,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13711AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13711AC\"></sup>turned aside from following Him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13711AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13711AD\"></sup>had no regard for any of His ways;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So that they caused <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13712AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13712AE\"></sup>the cry of the poor to come to Him,And that He might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13712AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13712AF\"></sup>hear the cry of the afflicted—",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When He keeps quiet, who then can condemn?And when He hides His face, who then can behold Him,That is, in regard to both nation and man?—",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13714AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13714AG\"></sup>godless men would not ruleNor be snares of the people.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“For has anyone said to God,‘I have borne <i>chastisement</i>;I will not offend <i>anymore</i>;",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Teach me what I do not see;If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13716AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13716AH\"></sup>done iniquity,I will not do it again’?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Shall He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13717AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13717AI\"></sup>recompense on your terms, because you have rejected <i>it</i>?For you must choose, and not I;Therefore declare what you know.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Men of understanding will say to me,And a wise man who hears me,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>‘Job <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13719AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13719AJ\"></sup>speaks without knowledge,And his words are without wisdom.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>‘Job ought to be tried to the limit,Because he answers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13720AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13720AK\"></sup>like wicked men.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>‘For he adds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13721AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13721AL\"></sup>rebellion to his sin;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13721AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13721AM\"></sup>claps his hands among us,And multiplies his words against God.’”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>Then Elihu continued and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Do you think this is according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13723A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13723A\"></sup>justice?Do you say, ‘My righteousness is more than God’s’?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For you say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13724B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13724B\"></sup>What advantage will it be to You?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13724C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13724C\"></sup>What profit will I have, more than if I had sinned?’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I will answer you,And your friends with you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13726D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13726D\"></sup>Look at the heavens and see;And behold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13726E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13726E\"></sup>the clouds—they are higher than you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“If you have sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13727F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13727F\"></sup>what do you accomplish against Him?And if your transgressions are many, what do you do to Him?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“If you are righteous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13728G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13728G\"></sup>what do you give to Him,Or what does He receive from your hand?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Your wickedness is for a man like yourself,And your righteousness is for a son of man.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13730H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13730H\"></sup>multitude of oppressions they cry out;They cry for help because of the arm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13730I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13730I\"></sup>of the mighty.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13731J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13731J\"></sup>no one says, ‘Where is God my Maker,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13731K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13731K\"></sup>gives songs in the night,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13732L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13732L\"></sup>teaches us more than the beasts of the earthAnd makes us wiser than the birds of the heavens?’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“There <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13733M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13733M\"></sup>they cry out, but He does not answerBecause of the pride of evil men.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13734N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13734N\"></sup>God will not listen to an empty <i>cry</i>,Nor will the Almighty regard it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“How much less when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13735O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13735O\"></sup>you say you do not behold Him,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13735P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13735P\"></sup>case is before Him, and you must wait for Him!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“And now, because He has not visited <i>in</i> His anger,Nor has He acknowledged transgression well,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So Job opens his mouth emptily;He multiplies words <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13737Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13737Q\"></sup>without knowledge.”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>Then Elihu continued and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Wait for me a little, and I will show youThat there is yet more to be said in God’s behalf.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I will fetch my knowledge from afar,And I will ascribe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13740A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13740A\"></sup>righteousness to my Maker.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13741B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13741B\"></sup>my words are not false;One who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13741C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13741C\"></sup>perfect in knowledge is with you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Behold, God is mighty but does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13742D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13742D\"></sup>despise <i>any</i>;<i>He is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13742E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13742E\"></sup>mighty in strength of understanding.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“He does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13743F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13743F\"></sup>keep the wicked alive,But gives justice to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13743G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13743G\"></sup>the afflicted.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“He does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13744H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13744H\"></sup>withdraw His eyes from the righteous;But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13744I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13744I\"></sup>with kings on the throneHe has seated them forever, and they are exalted.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And if they are bound in fetters,And are caught in the cords of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13745J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13745J\"></sup>affliction,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then He declares to them their workAnd their transgressions, that they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13746K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13746K\"></sup>magnified themselves.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13747L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13747L\"></sup>He opens their ear to instruction,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13747M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13747M\"></sup>commands that they return from evil.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“If they hear and serve <i>Him</i>,They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13748N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13748N\"></sup>end their days in prosperityAnd their years in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13748O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13748O\"></sup>pleasures.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But if they do not hear, they shall perish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13749P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13749P\"></sup>by the swordAnd they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13749Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13749Q\"></sup>die without knowledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“But the godless in heart lay up anger;They do not cry for help when He binds them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“They die in youth,And their life <i>perishes</i> among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13751R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13751R\"></sup>cult prostitutes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“He delivers the afflicted in their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13752S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13752S\"></sup>affliction,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13752T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13752T\"></sup>opens their ear in <i>time of</i> oppression.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Then indeed, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13753U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13753U\"></sup>enticed you from the mouth of distress,Instead of it, a broad place with no constraint;And that which was set on your table was full of fatness.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But you were full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13754V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13754V\"></sup>judgment on the wicked;Judgment and justice take hold <i>of you</i>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<i>Beware</i> that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13755W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13755W\"></sup>wrath does not entice you to scoffing;And do not let the greatness of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13755X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13755X\"></sup>ransom turn you aside.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Will your riches keep you from distress,Or all the forces of <i>your</i> strength?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Do not long for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13757Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13757Y\"></sup>the night,When people vanish in their place.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Be careful, do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13758Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13758Z\"></sup>not turn to evil,For you have preferred this to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13758AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13758AA\"></sup>affliction.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Behold, God is exalted in His power;Who is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13759AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13759AB\"></sup>teacher like Him?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Who has appointed Him His way,And who has said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13760AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13760AC\"></sup>You have done wrong’?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Remember that you should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13761AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13761AD\"></sup>exalt His work,Of which men have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13761AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13761AE\"></sup>sung.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“All men have seen it;Man beholds from afar.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Behold, God is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13763AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13763AF\"></sup>exalted, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13763AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13763AG\"></sup>we do not know <i>Him</i>;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13763AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13763AH\"></sup>number of His years is unsearchable.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13764AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13764AI\"></sup>He draws up the drops of water,They distill rain from the mist,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Which the clouds pour down,They drip upon man abundantly.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Can anyone understand the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13766AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13766AJ\"></sup>spreading of the clouds,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13766AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13766AK\"></sup>thundering of His pavilion?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Behold, He spreads His lightning about Him,And He covers the depths of the sea.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“For by these He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13768AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13768AL\"></sup>judges peoples;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13768AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13768AM\"></sup>gives food in abundance.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“He covers <i>His</i> hands with the lightning,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13769AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13769AN\"></sup>commands it to strike the mark.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13770AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13770AO\"></sup>noise declares His presence;The cattle also, concerning what is coming up."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>“At this also my heart trembles,And leaps from its place.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Listen closely to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13772A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13772A\"></sup>thunder of His voice,And the rumbling that goes out from His mouth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Under the whole heaven He lets it loose,And His lightning to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13773B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13773B\"></sup>ends of the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“After it, a voice roars;He thunders with His majestic voice,And He does not restrain the lightnings when His voice is heard.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13775C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13775C\"></sup>thunders with His voice wondrously,Doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13775D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13775D\"></sup>great things which we cannot comprehend.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13776E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13776E\"></sup>the snow He says, ‘Fall on the earth,’And to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13776F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13776F\"></sup>downpour and the rain, ‘Be strong.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13777G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13777G\"></sup>seals the hand of every man,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13777H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13777H\"></sup>all men may know His work.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Then the beast goes into its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13778I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13778I\"></sup>lairAnd remains in its den.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13779J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13779J\"></sup>south comes the storm,And out of the north the cold.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“From the breath of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13780K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13780K\"></sup>ice is made,And the expanse of the waters is frozen.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Also with moisture He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13781L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13781L\"></sup>loads the thick cloud;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13781M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13781M\"></sup>disperses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13781N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13781N\"></sup>the cloud of His lightning.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“It changes direction, turning around by His guidance,That it may do whatever He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13782O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13782O\"></sup>commands itOn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13782P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13782P\"></sup>face of the inhabited earth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Whether for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13783Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13783Q\"></sup>correction, or for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13783R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13783R\"></sup>His world,Or for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13783S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13783S\"></sup>lovingkindness, He causes it to happen.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Listen to this, O Job,Stand and consider the wonders of God.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Do you know how God establishes them,And makes the lightning of His cloud to shine?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Do you know about the layers of the thick clouds,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13786T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13786T\"></sup>wonders of one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13786U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13786U\"></sup>perfect in knowledge,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You whose garments are hot,When the land is still because of the south wind?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Can you, with Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13788V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13788V\"></sup>spread out the skies,Strong as a molten mirror?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Teach us what we shall say to Him;We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13789W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13789W\"></sup>cannot arrange <i>our case</i> because of darkness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Shall it be told Him that I would speak?Or should a man say that he would be swallowed up?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Now men do not see the light which is bright in the skies;But the wind has passed and cleared them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Out of the north comes golden <i>splendor</i>;Around God is awesome majesty.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“The Almighty—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13793X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13793X\"></sup>we cannot find Him;He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13793Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13793Y\"></sup>exalted in powerAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13793Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13793Z\"></sup>He will not do violence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13793AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13793AA\"></sup>to justice and abundant righteousness.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Therefore men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13794AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13794AB\"></sup>fear Him;He does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13794AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13794AC\"></sup>regard any who are wise of heart.”"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13795A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13795A\"></sup>answered Job out of the whirlwind and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Who is this that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13796B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13796B\"></sup>darkens counselBy words without knowledge?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13797C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13797C\"></sup>gird up your loins like a man,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13797D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13797D\"></sup>I will ask you, and you instruct Me!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Where were you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13798E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13798E\"></sup>when I laid the foundation of the earth?Tell <i>Me</i>, if you have understanding,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who set its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13799F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13799F\"></sup>measurements? Since you know.Or who stretched the line on it?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“On what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13800G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13800G\"></sup>were its bases sunk?Or who laid its cornerstone,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the morning stars sang togetherAnd all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13801H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13801H\"></sup>sons of God shouted for joy?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Or <i>who</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13802I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13802I\"></sup>enclosed the sea with doorsWhen, bursting forth, it went out from the womb;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When I made a cloud its garmentAnd thick darkness its swaddling band,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13804J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13804J\"></sup>placed boundaries on itAnd set a bolt and doors,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And I said, ‘Thus far you shall come, but no farther;And here shall your proud waves stop’?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Have you ever in your life commanded the morning,<i>And</i> caused the dawn to know its place,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>That it might take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13807K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13807K\"></sup>the ends of the earth,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13807L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13807L\"></sup>the wicked be shaken out of it?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“It is changed like clay <i>under</i> the seal;And they stand forth like a garment.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13809M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13809M\"></sup>From the wicked their light is withheld,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13809N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13809N\"></sup>uplifted arm is broken.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Have you entered into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13810O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13810O\"></sup>the springs of the seaOr walked in the recesses of the deep?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Have the gates of death been revealed to you,Or have you seen the gates of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13811P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13811P\"></sup>deep darkness?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Have you understood the expanse of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13812Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13812Q\"></sup>the earth?Tell <i>Me</i>, if you know all this.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Where is the way to the dwelling of light?And darkness, where is its place,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>That you may take it to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13814R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13814R\"></sup>its territoryAnd that you may discern the paths to its home?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“You know, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13815S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13815S\"></sup>you were born then,And the number of your days is great!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Have you entered the storehouses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13816T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13816T\"></sup>of the snow,Or have you seen the storehouses of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13816U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13816U\"></sup>hail,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Which I have reserved for the time of distress,For the day of war and battle?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Where is the way that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13818V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13818V\"></sup>the light is divided,<i>Or</i> the east wind scattered on the earth?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Who has cleft a channel for the flood,Or a way for the thunderbolt,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>To bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13820W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13820W\"></sup>rain on a land without people,<i>On</i> a desert without a man in it,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13821X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13821X\"></sup>satisfy the waste and desolate landAnd to make the seeds of grass to sprout?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13822Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13822Y\"></sup>the rain a father?Or who has begotten the drops of dew?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“From whose womb has come the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13823Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13823Z\"></sup>ice?And the frost of heaven, who has given it birth?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Water becomes hard like stone,And the surface of the deep is imprisoned.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Can you bind the chains of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13825AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13825AA\"></sup>Pleiades,Or loose the cords of Orion?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Can you lead forth a constellation in its season,And guide the Bear with her satellites?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Do you know the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13827AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13827AB\"></sup>ordinances of the heavens,Or fix their rule over the earth?",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Can you lift up your voice to the clouds,So that an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13828AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13828AC\"></sup>abundance of water will cover you?",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“Can you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13829AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13829AD\"></sup>send forth lightnings that they may goAnd say to you, ‘Here we are’?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13830AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13830AE\"></sup>put wisdom in the innermost beingOr given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13830AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13830AF\"></sup>understanding to the mind?",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“Who can count the clouds by wisdom,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13831AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13831AG\"></sup>tip the water jars of the heavens,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>When the dust hardens into a massAnd the clods stick together?",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“Can you hunt the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13833AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13833AH\"></sup>prey for the lion,Or satisfy the appetite of the young lions,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>When they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13834AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13834AI\"></sup>crouch in <i>their</i> dens<i>And</i> lie in wait in <i>their</i> lair?",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“Who prepares for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13835AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13835AJ\"></sup>the raven its nourishmentWhen its young cry to GodAnd wander about without food?"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>“Do you know the time the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13836A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13836A\"></sup>mountain goats give birth?Do you observe the calving of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13836B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13836B\"></sup>deer?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Can you count the months they fulfill,Or do you know the time they give birth?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“They kneel down, they bring forth their young,They get rid of their labor pains.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Their offspring become strong, they grow up in the open field;They leave and do not return to them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Who sent out the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13840C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13840C\"></sup>wild donkey free?And who loosed the bonds of the swift donkey,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>To whom I gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13841D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13841D\"></sup>the wilderness for a homeAnd the salt land for his dwelling place?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“He scorns the tumult of the city,The shoutings of the driver he does not hear.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“He explores the mountains for his pastureAnd searches after every green thing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Will the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13844E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13844E\"></sup>wild ox consent to serve you,Or will he spend the night at your manger?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Can you bind the wild ox in a furrow with ropes,Or will he harrow the valleys after you?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Will you trust him because his strength is greatAnd leave your labor to him?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Will you have faith in him that he will return your grainAnd gather <i>it from</i> your threshing floor?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The ostriches’ wings flap joyouslyWith the pinion and plumage of love,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For she abandons her eggs to the earthAnd warms them in the dust,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And she forgets that a foot may crush them,Or that a wild beast may trample them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“She treats her young <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13851F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13851F\"></sup>cruelly, as if <i>they</i> were not hers;Though her labor be in vain, <i>she</i> is unconcerned;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because God has made her forget wisdom,And has not given her a share of understanding.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“When she lifts herself on high,She laughs at the horse and his rider.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Do you give the horse <i>his</i> might?Do you clothe his neck with a mane?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Do you make him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13855G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13855G\"></sup>leap like the locust?His majestic <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13855H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13855H\"></sup>snorting is terrible.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“He paws in the valley, and rejoices in <i>his</i> strength;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13856I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13856I\"></sup>goes out to meet the weapons.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“He laughs at fear and is not dismayed;And he does not turn back from the sword.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“The quiver rattles against him,The flashing spear and javelin.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“With shaking and rage he races over the ground,And he does not stand still at the voice of the trumpet.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“As often as the trumpet <i>sounds</i> he says, ‘Aha!’And he scents the battle from afar,And the thunder of the captains and the war cry.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Is it by your understanding that the hawk soars,Stretching his wings toward the south?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Is it at your command that the eagle mounts upAnd makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13862J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13862J\"></sup>his nest on high?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“On the cliff he dwells and lodges,Upon the rocky crag, an inaccessible place.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“From there he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13864K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13864K\"></sup>spies out food;His eyes see <i>it</i> from afar.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“His young ones also suck up blood;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13865L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13865L\"></sup>where the slain are, there is he.”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Job,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Will the faultfinder <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13867A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13867A\"></sup>contend with the Almighty?Let him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13867B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13867B\"></sup>reproves God answer it.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Job answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Behold, I am insignificant; what can I reply to You?I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13869C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13869C\"></sup>lay my hand on my mouth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Once I have spoken, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13870D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13870D\"></sup>I will not answer;Even twice, and I will add nothing more.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13871E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13871E\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered Job out of the storm and said,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13872F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13872F\"></sup>gird up your loins like a man;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13872G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13872G\"></sup>ask you, and you instruct Me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Will you really <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13873H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13873H\"></sup>annul My judgment?Will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13873I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13873I\"></sup>condemn Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13873J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13873J\"></sup>that you may be justified?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Or do you have an arm like God,And can you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13874K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13874K\"></sup>thunder with a voice like His?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13875L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13875L\"></sup>Adorn yourself with eminence and dignity,And clothe yourself with honor and majesty.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Pour out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13876M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13876M\"></sup>the overflowings of your anger,And look on everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13876N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13876N\"></sup>proud, and make him low.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Look on everyone who is proud, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13877O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13877O\"></sup>humble him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13877P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13877P\"></sup>tread down the wicked where they stand.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13878Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13878Q\"></sup>Hide them in the dust together;Bind them in the hidden <i>place</i>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Then I will also confess to you,That your own right hand can save you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Behold now, Behemoth, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13880R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13880R\"></sup>I made as well as you;He eats grass like an ox.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Behold now, his strength in his loinsAnd his power in the muscles of his belly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“He bends his tail like a cedar;The sinews of his thighs are knit together.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“His bones are tubes of bronze;His limbs are like bars of iron.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13884S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13884S\"></sup>first of the ways of God;Let his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13884T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13884T\"></sup>maker bring near his sword.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Surely the mountains <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13885U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13885U\"></sup>bring him food,And all the beasts of the field <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13885V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13885V\"></sup>play there.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Under the lotus plants he lies down,In the covert of the reeds and the marsh.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“The lotus plants cover him with shade;The willows of the brook surround him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“If a river rages, he is not alarmed;He is confident, though the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13888W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13888W\"></sup>Jordan rushes to his mouth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Can anyone capture him when he is on watch,With barbs can anyone pierce <i>his</i> nose?"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>“Can you draw out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13890A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13890A\"></sup>Leviathan with a fishhook?Or press down his tongue with a cord?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Can you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13891B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13891B\"></sup>put a rope in his noseOr pierce his jaw with a hook?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Will he make many supplications to you,Or will he speak to you soft words?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Will he make a covenant with you?Will you take him for a servant forever?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Will you play with him as with a bird,Or will you bind him for your maidens?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Will the traders bargain over him?Will they divide him among the merchants?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Can you fill his skin with harpoons,Or his head with fishing spears?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Lay your hand on him;Remember the battle; you will not do it again!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Behold, your expectation is false;Will you be laid low even at the sight of him?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“No one is so fierce that he dares to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13899C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13899C\"></sup>arouse him;Who then is he that can stand before Me?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13900D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13900D\"></sup>given to Me that I should repay <i>him</i>?<i>Whatever</i> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13900E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13900E\"></sup>under the whole heaven is Mine.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will not keep silence concerning his limbs,Or his mighty strength, or his orderly frame.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Who can strip off his outer armor?Who can come within his double mail?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Who can open the doors of his face?Around his teeth there is terror.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<i>His</i> strong scales are <i>his</i> pride,Shut up <i>as with</i> a tight seal.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“One is so near to anotherThat no air can come between them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“They are joined one to another;They clasp each other and cannot be separated.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“His sneezes flash forth light,And his eyes are like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13907F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13907F\"></sup>eyelids of the morning.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Out of his mouth go burning torches;Sparks of fire leap forth.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Out of his nostrils smoke goes forthAs <i>from</i> a boiling pot and <i>burning</i> rushes.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“His breath kindles coals,And a flame goes forth from his mouth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“In his neck lodges strength,And dismay leaps before him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“The folds of his flesh are joined together,Firm on him and immovable.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“His heart is as hard as a stone,Even as hard as a lower millstone.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“When he raises himself up, the mighty fear;Because of the crashing they are bewildered.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“The sword that reaches him cannot avail,Nor the spear, the dart or the javelin.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“He regards iron as straw,Bronze as rotten wood.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“The arrow cannot make him flee;Slingstones are turned into stubble for him.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Clubs are regarded as stubble;He laughs at the rattling of the javelin.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“His underparts are <i>like</i> sharp potsherds;He spreads out <i>like</i> a threshing sledge on the mire.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“He makes the depths boil like a pot;He makes the sea like a jar of ointment.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Behind him he makes a wake to shine;One would think the deep to be gray-haired.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13922G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13922G\"></sup>Nothing on earth is like him,One made without fear.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“He looks on everything that is high;He is king over all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13923H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13923H\"></sup>sons of pride.”"
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then Job answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13925A\"></sup>You can do all things,And that no purpose of Yours can be thwarted.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘Who is this that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13926B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13926B\"></sup>hides counsel without knowledge?’Therefore I have declared that which I did not understand,Things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13926C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13926C\"></sup>too wonderful for me, which I did not know.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘Hear, now, and I will speak;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13927D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13927D\"></sup>ask You, and You instruct me.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13928E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13928E\"></sup>heard of You by the hearing of the ear;But now my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13928F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13928F\"></sup>eye sees You;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore I retract,And I repent in dust and ashes.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It came about after the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had spoken these words to Job, that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Eliphaz the Temanite, “My wrath is kindled against you and against your two friends, because you have not spoken of Me what is right <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13930G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13930G\"></sup>as My servant Job has.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now therefore, take for yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13931H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13931H\"></sup>seven bulls and seven rams, and go to My servant Job, and offer up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13931I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13931I\"></sup>burnt offering for yourselves, and My servant Job will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13931J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13931J\"></sup>pray for you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13931K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13931K\"></sup>For I will accept him so that I may not do with you <i>according to your</i> folly, because you have not spoken of Me what is right, as My servant Job has.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So Eliphaz the Temanite and Bildad the Shuhite <i>and</i> Zophar the Naamathite went and did as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> told them; and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> accepted Job.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13933L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13933L\"></sup>restored the fortunes of Job when he prayed for his friends, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> increased all that Job had twofold.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then all his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13934M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13934M\"></sup>brothers and all his sisters and all who had known him before came to him, and they ate bread with him in his house; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13934N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13934N\"></sup>consoled him and comforted him for all the adversities that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had brought on him. And each one gave him one piece of money, and each a ring of gold.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13935O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13935O\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> blessed the latter <i>days</i> of Job more than his beginning; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13935P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13935P\"></sup>and he had 14,000 sheep and 6,000 camels and 1,000 yoke of oxen and 1,000 female donkeys.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13936Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13936Q\"></sup>He had seven sons and three daughters.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He named the first Jemimah, and the second Keziah, and the third Keren-happuch.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In all the land no women were found so fair as Job’s daughters; and their father gave them inheritance among their brothers.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>After this, Job lived 140 years, and saw his sons and his grandsons, four generations.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-13940R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-13940R\"></sup>And Job died, an old man and full of days."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;